{"type":"message","id":"cb552ed4","parentId":"c9a1f942","timestamp":"2026-04-14T02:06:21.685Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a much better picture. Let me understand the issue:\n\n1. The `ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.json` was generated on 2026-04-01 16:37:49 (13 days ago), exceeding the 24-hour max age\n2. The skill `a-share-fusion-report` checks for stale source files before running\n3. Tushare token IS configured in `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/.env` as `TUSHARE_TOKEN=e3d8c68a414b9a84cbc49c637ec00875c7173a961eba98cff09c1afc`\n\n\n4. The real-time data probe from this morning shows degraded status with Tushare token not actually being consumed by the system despite being configured, and SSL certificate issues preventing real-time price retrieval\n\nSo the problem is that the Tushare token exists but isn't being properly utilized in the data pipeline, which is why we're getting staleness warnings and degraded data quality. I'm tracing through the data flow more carefully now. The `web_source_fusion_daily_latest.json` is checking the age of `ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.json` and finding it stale (24+ hours old), which is causing the FAILED_CLOSED status. But when I look at the overlay task output from 09:21, it shows the script actually ran successfully—it's just that SSL certificate problems prevented real-time price fetching, yet the analysis still completed. This seems contradictory to the stale file error I'm seeing in the logs. 所以问题可能不在 overlay 脚本本身，而是在检查数据新鲜度的验证逻辑。我需要找出是哪个脚本在写入 `web_source_fusion_daily_latest.json` 并检查 `ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.json` 的有效期，然后修复数据源更新的问题。\n\n张玲早上已经接通了同花顺的 Level 2 行情，并且给了我 Tushare token，所以我需要用这个 token 来修复数据源。同时还要处理那只 1.95% 价差分歧的 301018 申菱环境股票，确保系统能正确获取实时价格。 数据源价差分歧 > 0.8%\n\nTushare token 是昨天给的，但系统没有使用它。需要确保 Tushare token 被正确加载到 `daily_stock_analysis_upgrade_preview` 项目的配置中。\n\n让我检查 `src/config.py` 中如何加载 `TUSHARE_TOKEN`。\n\n主要问题：\n1. `ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.json` 文件太旧（4月1日的）\n2. 实时价格因 SSL 证书问题获取失败\n3. Tushare token 未被使用\n\n我需要：\n1. 确保 `TUSHARE_TOKEN` 环境变量被设置\n2. 重新获取同花顺投资账本的最新数据（ths_web_selected_holdings）\n3. 重新运行 overlay 分析\n\n让我先检查环境变量和配置。\n","thinkingSignature":"4997cb5fd7d944a6dd6f5fd51377dc68d2404e3e30d7aad95a8537c6eb2adae8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yyehxrj6a650_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"source /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/.env 2>/dev/null; echo \"TUSHARE_TOKEN=$TUSHARE_TOKEN\" && python3 -c \"import os; print('TUSHARE_TOKEN from env:', os.getenv('TUSHARE_TOKEN','NOT SET'))\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yyehxrj6a650_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport sys\nsys.path.insert(0, '/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis_upgrade_preview')\nfrom src.config import get_config\ncfg = get_config()\nprint('tushare_token:', repr(cfg.tushare_token))\nprint('realtime_source_priority:', cfg.realtime_source_priority)\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1515,"output":782,"cacheRead":69952,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72249,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776132352881,"responseId":"062cd402a70d9afa91a0b72d5892ecf2"}}
{"type":"message","id":"929a621c","parentId":"cb552ed4","timestamp":"2026-04-14T02:06:22.783Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_yyehxrj6a650_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"TUSHARE_TOKEN=e3d8c68a414b9a84cbc49c637ec00875c7173a961eba98cff09c1afc\nTUSHARE_TOKEN from env: NOT SET"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":838,"aggregated":"TUSHARE_TOKEN=e3d8c68a414b9a84cbc49c637ec00875c7173a961eba98cff09c1afc\nTUSHARE_TOKEN from env: NOT SET","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776132382777}}
