{"type":"message","id":"36a47366","parentId":"cc8a039f","timestamp":"2026-04-14T02:16:14.321Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, the holdings list has 36 items but the selected_real_positions_20260414.csv from before had 23 items (matching the ths_web_selected_holdings from April 1). The ths_selected_holdings.json from coding-agent has 36 items including HK stocks and funds.\n\nThe overlay system needs 23 A-share holdings (the confirmed real A-share holdings from ths_web_selected_holdings), not all 36 including HK/funds. Let me re-read the original selected_real_positions_20260414.csv content:\n\n```\nsymbol,asset_type,name,quantity,cost_price\n300500.SZ,stock,启迪设计,8000,13.111\n002963.SZ,stock,豪尔赛,1300,15.881\n...\n```\n\nSo the original had 23 rows of just A-share stocks. The ths_selected_holdings.json has 36 items including HK stocks, funds. The filtering should be asset_type=stock + symbol ending in .SH/.SZ/.BJ.\n\n\nI need to filter the ths_selected_holdings.json data to include only A-share stocks and recreate the CSV with just those entries.\n","thinkingSignature":"2081fa1fc6cb5317da21012e679602a0bece99007f40fb03e9d0fc67e13dd065"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rpjqo5q38611_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nfrom pathlib import Path\nimport json, csv\n\n# 读取coding-agent目录下4月9日更新的THS本地持仓\nths_json = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent/ths_selected_holdings.json')\nd = json.load(open(ths_json))\nholdings = d.get('holdings', [])\n\n# 过滤：只保留A股（stock类型，symbol以.SZ/.SH/.BJ结尾）\na_share_rows = []\nfor h in holdings:\n    sym = h.get('symbol','')\n    asset_type = h.get('asset_type','')\n    if asset_type == 'stock' and sym.endswith(('.SZ', '.SH', '.BJ')):\n        a_share_rows.append({\n            'symbol': sym,\n            'asset_type': 'stock',\n            'name': h.get('name',''),\n            'quantity': h.get('quantity',''),\n            'cost_price': h.get('cost_price','')\n        })\n\nprint(f'A-share rows: {len(a_share_rows)}')\n\nreport_dir = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports')\ntoday_csv = report_dir / 'selected_real_positions_20260414.csv'\nlatest_csv = report_dir / 'selected_real_positions_latest.csv'\n\nwith open(today_csv, 'w', newline='', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    writer = csv.DictWriter(f, fieldnames=['symbol','asset_type','name','quantity','cost_price'])\n    writer.writeheader()\n    writer.writerows(a_share_rows)\n\nimport shutil\nshutil.copyfile(today_csv, latest_csv)\nprint(f'Written {len(a_share_rows)} A-share rows')\nprint('First 5:', [r['symbol'] for r in a_share_rows[:5]])\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":478,"output":641,"cacheRead":89152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90271,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776132951257,"responseId":"062cd6588059280360fb7542146ab1d9"}}
