{"type":"message","id":"65e55ff5","parentId":"76a7c35d","timestamp":"2026-04-14T03:22:17.334Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，fusion report运行成功了，数据来自4月8日的ths_app_holdings文件（而非最新的THS本地账本）。价格数据已经通过Tushare获取到了（不再是SSL问题）。\n\nfeishu push失败是因为appId/appSecret没有配置，但这是skill层面的问题。\n\n现在让我给张玲一个完整的回复：\n1. 告诉她我已经修复了Tushare实时价格问题\n2. fusion report已成功运行\n3. 关于JoinQuant文章，我需要用其他工具来获取\n\n同时我还需要处理那篇文章。让我用web-pilot skill来获取文章内容。\n","thinkingSignature":"a9c7694540f0f35ed8da0e77fd727cad21ad0327f828312b5ed41cf696c8485a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_eay82tn5pmrt_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 用web-pilot获取JoinQuant文章\ncd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace && python3 -c \"\nimport sys\nsys.path.insert(0, 'skills/web-pilot')\n\" 2>/dev/null; echo \"done\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_eay82tn5pmrt_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/web-pilot/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1211,"output":231,"cacheRead":96704,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98146,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776136922576,"responseId":"062ce5dd1c122867aece848086e39493"}}
