{"type":"message","id":"ad05e09f","parentId":"35ade908","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:56:30.990Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the full picture. The cron for intraday recheck (which sends push notifications) is not installed. The cron only has:\n- 09:35: sync sector board + premarket precheck\n- 08:30: cron_breadth_paper_trading.sh\n- 08:25: cron_paper_trading_profiles_v1.sh (which failed due to SSL check issue)\n\nThe intraday recheck cron is NOT in crontab. But wait - maybe the user is referring to a different \"模拟盘买卖记录推送\". Let me check what the intraday recheck script does.\n","thinkingSignature":"fcdba49b48e700dcae56e9a49ec71f98408f06d018ec7f02e9e15eb03fa27c32"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5vaie9poi41t_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"head -50 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_intraday_risk_recheck.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5vaie9poi41t_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"push\\|feishu\\|send\\|notify\\|买卖\\|signal\\|paper_trade\\|fill\\|order\" /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_intraday_risk_recheck.py 2>/dev/null | head -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":433,"output":266,"cacheRead":103488,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104187,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776153377791,"responseId":"062d2624c33e771d69dff09abecc921b"}}
