{"type":"message","id":"53da0179","parentId":"149c62bf","timestamp":"2026-04-14T07:56:54.603Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The intraday recheck script doesn't directly send paper trade signals. It just does risk recheck and sends alerts if something is wrong. The actual paper trading signals are generated by `run_live_execution_v1.py` or by the `cron_paper_trading_profiles_v1.sh` and `cron_breadth_paper_trading.sh` scripts.\n\nBut those scripts all check the market day with the SSL-problematic qt.gtimg.cn API. Since the cron script uses `python3` directly (not the `cron_python.sh` wrapper which might have SSL fix), it fails at the market check and skips the entire run.\n\nThe key finding:\n1. `cron_paper_trading_profiles_v1.sh` uses `python3 -c` with `urllib.request.urlopen` to `qt.gtimg.cn`\n\n\n2. This fails with SSL certificate verification error\n3. The script falls back to `print('yes')` which causes it to say \"非 A 股交易日\" and exit early\n4. This means all paper trading profiles and signals for today were skipped\n\nNow I need to fix the SSL issue and re-run the trading signals for today. First, I should check what signals were actually generated.\n","thinkingSignature":"98d3fbe6d8d62aa37b3390375dd302a22533ae23dd5253263ff537c5f70f6653"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ua6xbkn5x9gb_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查今天所有盘中实际生成的报告\nls -la /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/*20260414*.json 2>/dev/null | head -20\necho \"---\"\nls -la /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/auto_premarket_precheck_20260414.json 2>/dev/null"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ua6xbkn5x9gb_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/auto_premarket_precheck_20260414.json 2>/dev/null | python3 -c \"import json,sys; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(json.dumps({k:v for k,v in d.items() if k not in ['position_signals','candidate_signals','overlay_report_content','market_context']}, indent=2))\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":723,"output":488,"cacheRead":103872,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":105083,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776153391125,"responseId":"062d2631ea5a6a57ab0247022d33417c"}}
