{"type":"message","id":"fe706fb8","parentId":"5e9f2466","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:14:37.362Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The MKT_OK check actually uses `http://` (not `https://`) so SSL is not the issue there! Let me re-examine what actually caused the \"非 A 股交易日\" message. Maybe the script was checking with http but the URL returned old data? Let me look more carefully.\n\nActually wait - the script uses `http://qt.gtimg.cn/q=sh000001` (HTTP, not HTTPS). The SSL issue I saw earlier was with HTTPS. So the MKT_OK should work via HTTP.\n\nBut the log says \"非 A 股交易日\". Let me trace the actual error. The cron might have run but the `auto_run_premarket_precheck.py` was the one that actually produced today's precheck. \n\nThe cron ran at 08:25 and showed that message, which might mean the market wasn't detected as open, or the script exited early before reaching any market detection logic. I need to check what `cron_breadth_paper_trading.sh` actually does to understand the execution flow.\n","thinkingSignature":"b2650011aa547bebaddd25eb8873c58ac78c8b9270f15b74336658c8ca75ebb5"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_c01ubotxgek7_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/cron_breadth_paper_trading.sh"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":764,"output":266,"cacheRead":113280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114310,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776154463022,"responseId":"062d2a61ee80181b34ce9b0c352ebe37"}}
{"type":"message","id":"488a2e87","parentId":"fe706fb8","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:14:37.552Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_c01ubotxgek7_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env bash\nset -euo pipefail\n\nROOT=\"$(cd \"$(dirname \"$0\")/..\" && pwd)\"\ncd \"$ROOT\"\n\n# 非交易日跳过（qt.gtimg.cn 公开数据用 http 避免 Python 3.14 SSL 验证问题）\nMKT_DATE=$(python3 -c \"\nimport urllib.request, datetime\ntry:\n    req = urllib.request.Request('http://qt.gtimg.cn/q=sh000001', headers={'User-Agent':'Mozilla/5.0'})\n    with urllib.request.urlopen(req, timeout=5) as r:\n        c = r.read().decode('gbk', errors='replace')\n    for line in c.split(';'):\n        parts = line.split('~')\n        if len(parts) > 30:\n            mkt = parts[30].strip()[:8]\n            today = datetime.datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\n            if mkt != today:\n                exit(1)\n            exit(0)\n    exit(1)\nexcept:\n    exit(0)  # 网络异常时走cron 1-5兜底\n\" 2>/dev/null)\nif (($? != 0)); then\n    echo \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M')] 非 A 股交易日，跳过 breadth_aggressive_paper\"\n    exit 0\nfi\n\nPYRUN=\"$ROOT/scripts/cron_python.sh\"\n\"$PYRUN\" --runtime-only\n\n\"$PYRUN\" scripts/run_breadth_paper_trading.py"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":44,"aggregated":"#!/usr/bin/env bash\nset -euo pipefail\n\nROOT=\"$(cd \"$(dirname \"$0\")/..\" && pwd)\"\ncd \"$ROOT\"\n\n# 非交易日跳过（qt.gtimg.cn 公开数据用 http 避免 Python 3.14 SSL 验证问题）\nMKT_DATE=$(python3 -c \"\nimport urllib.request, datetime\ntry:\n    req = urllib.request.Request('http://qt.gtimg.cn/q=sh000001', headers={'User-Agent':'Mozilla/5.0'})\n    with urllib.request.urlopen(req, timeout=5) as r:\n        c = r.read().decode('gbk', errors='replace')\n    for line in c.split(';'):\n        parts = line.split('~')\n        if len(parts) > 30:\n            mkt = parts[30].strip()[:8]\n            today = datetime.datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\n            if mkt != today:\n                exit(1)\n            exit(0)\n    exit(1)\nexcept:\n    exit(0)  # 网络异常时走cron 1-5兜底\n\" 2>/dev/null)\nif (($? != 0)); then\n    echo \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M')] 非 A 股交易日，跳过 breadth_aggressive_paper\"\n    exit 0\nfi\n\nPYRUN=\"$ROOT/scripts/cron_python.sh\"\n\"$PYRUN\" --runtime-only\n\n\"$PYRUN\" scripts/run_breadth_paper_trading.py","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776154477530}}
