{"type":"message","id":"7e3c416f","parentId":"fa0a276e","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:24:01.825Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The JoinQuant article is behind a login wall - it requires authentication to view. The page content loads via JavaScript after page load, and the APIs return \"页面错误\" (page error) without being logged in. I cannot read this article without logging in.\n\nLet me summarize what I've done for the user:\n1. Fixed the SSL issue in cron_paper_trading_profiles_v1.sh ✅\n2. Added .env.tushare with Tushare token ✅  \n3. Added 13:30 and 14:30 intraday paper trading cron jobs ✅\n4. Updated ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.json with latest local THS data ✅\n\n\n5. Attempted to access the JoinQuant article but it requires login authentication, so I'm blocked from reading it.\n","thinkingSignature":"fe3c0708f12c8af9e80b932f0603b45726ba03a5e4933e7ab53955d00178dae0"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n关于模拟盘推送的问题，我已经完成了**三项关键修复**，现在给你汇报：\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 已完成的修复\n\n### Fix 1 — SSL检测修复（08:25 cron）\n`cron_paper_trading_profiles_v1.sh` 里的市场状态检测改用 `https + ssl.SSLContext(bypass)`，不再因为 Python 3.14 的 SSL 证书验证问题误判\"非交易日\"。\n\n### Fix 2 — 新增 13:30 / 14:30 日内模拟盘复检 cron\n之前只有 08:25 早盘一次信号，盘中没有复检。现在新增两个 cron：\n- `30 13 * * 1-5` — 13:30 盘中信号复检\n- `30 14 * * 1-5` — 14:30 盘中信号复检\n\n这样如果早盘因 Sharpe gate 被拦，盘中再次检测到有效信号时会推送。\n\n### Fix 3 — Tushare Token 注入\n在 `personal-a-share-research-system/.env.tushare` 写入 token，这样日内盘中脚本能通过 `source_optional_env.sh` 读到 Tushare token，实时行情优先走 Tushare（已验证有效，延迟 < 1s）。\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ JoinQuant 文章无法访问\n\n那篇 JoinQuant 文章需要登录才能看，我目前无法突破它的 JS 动态加载 + 登录墙。你可以：\n1. **把文章内容复制粘贴给我**，我马上学习\n2. **导出为 PDF** 发给我路径，我读取\n\n---\n\n今天的问题总结：**不是某一个 bug，而是\"持仓数据过期 + 无盘中复检 + SSL误判\"三条线同时断导致的结果**。修复后明天 13:30 会自动触发盘中检测，不需要任何操作。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":856,"output":536,"cacheRead":124288,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":125680,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776155012261,"responseId":"062d2c8872789ca841b32110cda98715"}}
