{"type":"message","id":"1f185be0","parentId":"479dad1b","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:27:29.531Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user confirmed they want me to learn this article. I've already read and analyzed it above. Let me acknowledge and confirm I've absorbed the key lessons, and note any system improvements I can make based on this.\n","thinkingSignature":"7b6449de0e398a488afe9234983847d03d4e87df23cadd57bd3dbf3eee89a625"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n[[reply_to_current]]\n\n已学习完毕，4个坑都很实在。总结一下我接下来要做的改进：\n\n---\n\n**过拟合压力测试自动化**\n每次策略调参后自动跑 5 年 OOS（2018-2022），改动任何一个参数都要过这关，否则打回。当前系统没有这一步，这是最大的隐患。\n\n**新增滑点 buffer**\n在 `run_live_execution_v1.py` 的信号处理链里，对所有实盘信号统一加 0.15% spread buffer，不显式建模但保守估计。\n\n**影子 → 灰度门槛**\nDual 因子现在 5 天数据跑赢了，需要设定\"至少 20 个交易日且夏普 > 1.0\"才能从 shadow 升级灰度，防止短期数字好看就上线。\n\n---\n\n这些都是今天的教训沉淀，干完我会通知你。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1548,"output":217,"cacheRead":133504,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":135269,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776155234580,"responseId":"062d2d6796a1d4c130e107fceccddc53"}}
