{"type":"message","id":"0ec6d4ff","parentId":"c6b6ca63","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:30:45.438Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_0h7kjs5u23rw_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport argparse\nimport copy\nimport json\nimport re\nimport sys\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nimport pandas as pd\n\nPROJECT_ROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[1]\nREPORT_DIR = PROJECT_ROOT / \"research\" / \"reports\"\nFORMAL_PARAMS_PATH = REPORT_DIR / \"dual_factor_formal_params.json\"\nROBUSTNESS_PATH = REPORT_DIR / \"dual_factor_robustness_report.json\"\nDEFAULT_SSE_INDEX_FILE = Path(\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis/index_000001_SH.csv\")\n\nfor candidate in [PROJECT_ROOT, PROJECT_ROOT / \"scripts\"]:\n    if str(candidate) not in sys.path:\n        sys.path.insert(0, str(candidate))\n\nimport numpy as np  # noqa: E402\nimport run_strategy_695_batch as batch  # noqa: E402\n\nPROFILE_DEFAULT = {\n    \"name\": \"default\",\n    \"roc10\": {\"window\": 10, \"bull\": 1.15, \"bear\": 0.85},\n    \"rsv5\": {\"window\": 5, \"median_window\": 60, \"median_min_periods\": 20, \"bull\": 1.10, \"bear\": 0.90},\n}\nPROFILE_CONSERVATIVE = {\n    \"name\": \"conservative\",\n    \"roc10\": {\"window\": 10, \"bull\": 1.10, \"bear\": 0.90},\n    \"rsv5\": {\"window\": 5, \"median_window\": 60, \"median_min_periods\": 20, \"bull\": 1.05, \"bear\": 0.95},\n}\n\n\ndef load_json(path: Path) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    return json.loads(path.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\n\n\ndef parse_float(text: str, default: float) -> float:\n    matches = re.findall(r\"([0-9]+(?:\\.[0-9]+)?)\", str(text or \"\"))\n    return float(matches[-1]) if matches else float(default)\n\n\ndef discover_latest_live_json() -> Path:\n    candidates = sorted(REPORT_DIR.glob(\"live_system_v1_*.json\"))\n    if not candidates:\n        raise FileNotFoundError(f\"未找到 live_system_v1_*.json: {REPORT_DIR}\")\n    return candidates[-1]\n\n\ndef normalize_metrics(series: pd.Series) -> dict[str, float | int]:\n    clean = series.dropna().astype(float)\n    if len(clean) == 0:\n        return {\n            \"ann_ret\": 0.0,\n            \"max_dd\": 0.0,\n            \"sharpe\": 0.0,\n            \"annual_vol\": 0.0,\n            \"final_equity\": 1.0,\n            \"n\": 0,\n        }\n    nav = (1.0 + clean).cumprod()\n    total = nav.iloc[-1] / nav.iloc[0] - 1.0\n    ann = (1.0 + total) ** (252.0 / len(clean)) - 1.0\n    max_dd = abs((nav / nav.cummax() - 1.0).min())\n    vol = clean.std() * np.sqrt(252.0)\n    sharpe = (clean.mean() * 252.0) / vol if vol > 0 else 0.0\n    return {\n        \"ann_ret\": round(float(ann * 100.0), 2),\n        \"max_dd\": round(float(max_dd * 100.0), 2),\n        \"sharpe\": round(float(sharpe), 3),\n        \"annual_vol\": round(float(vol * 100.0), 2),\n        \"final_equity\": round(float(nav.iloc[-1]), 4),\n        \"n\": int(len(clean)),\n    }"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":6,"aggregated":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport argparse\nimport copy\nimport json\nimport re\nimport sys\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nimport pandas as pd\n\nPROJECT_ROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[1]\nREPORT_DIR = PROJECT_ROOT / \"research\" / \"reports\"\nFORMAL_PARAMS_PATH = REPORT_DIR / \"dual_factor_formal_params.json\"\nROBUSTNESS_PATH = REPORT_DIR / \"dual_factor_robustness_report.json\"\nDEFAULT_SSE_INDEX_FILE = Path(\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis/index_000001_SH.csv\")\n\nfor candidate in [PROJECT_ROOT, PROJECT_ROOT / \"scripts\"]:\n    if str(candidate) not in sys.path:\n        sys.path.insert(0, str(candidate))\n\nimport numpy as np  # noqa: E402\nimport run_strategy_695_batch as batch  # noqa: E402\n\nPROFILE_DEFAULT = {\n    \"name\": \"default\",\n    \"roc10\": {\"window\": 10, \"bull\": 1.15, \"bear\": 0.85},\n    \"rsv5\": {\"window\": 5, \"median_window\": 60, \"median_min_periods\": 20, \"bull\": 1.10, \"bear\": 0.90},\n}\nPROFILE_CONSERVATIVE = {\n    \"name\": \"conservative\",\n    \"roc10\": {\"window\": 10, \"bull\": 1.10, \"bear\": 0.90},\n    \"rsv5\": {\"window\": 5, \"median_window\": 60, \"median_min_periods\": 20, \"bull\": 1.05, \"bear\": 0.95},\n}\n\n\ndef load_json(path: Path) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    return json.loads(path.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\n\n\ndef parse_float(text: str, default: float) -> float:\n    matches = re.findall(r\"([0-9]+(?:\\.[0-9]+)?)\", str(text or \"\"))\n    return float(matches[-1]) if matches else float(default)\n\n\ndef discover_latest_live_json() -> Path:\n    candidates = sorted(REPORT_DIR.glob(\"live_system_v1_*.json\"))\n    if not candidates:\n        raise FileNotFoundError(f\"未找到 live_system_v1_*.json: {REPORT_DIR}\")\n    return candidates[-1]\n\n\ndef normalize_metrics(series: pd.Series) -> dict[str, float | int]:\n    clean = series.dropna().astype(float)\n    if len(clean) == 0:\n        return {\n            \"ann_ret\": 0.0,\n            \"max_dd\": 0.0,\n            \"sharpe\": 0.0,\n            \"annual_vol\": 0.0,\n            \"final_equity\": 1.0,\n            \"n\": 0,\n        }\n    nav = (1.0 + clean).cumprod()\n    total = nav.iloc[-1] / nav.iloc[0] - 1.0\n    ann = (1.0 + total) ** (252.0 / len(clean)) - 1.0\n    max_dd = abs((nav / nav.cummax() - 1.0).min())\n    vol = clean.std() * np.sqrt(252.0)\n    sharpe = (clean.mean() * 252.0) / vol if vol > 0 else 0.0\n    return {\n        \"ann_ret\": round(float(ann * 100.0), 2),\n        \"max_dd\": round(float(max_dd * 100.0), 2),\n        \"sharpe\": round(float(sharpe), 3),\n        \"annual_vol\": round(float(vol * 100.0), 2),\n        \"final_equity\": round(float(nav.iloc[-1]), 4),\n        \"n\": int(len(clean)),\n    }","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776155445429}}
{"type":"message","id":"9a13d02b","parentId":"0ec6d4ff","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:31:05.595Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture of the system. Let me implement the three improvements:\n\n1. **滑点 buffer** - Add to `run_live_execution_v1.py` where ref_price is used\n2. **过拟合压力测试** - Create a new script `scripts/strategy_overfit_gate.py` \n3. **影子升级门槛** - Add to `run_live_system_v1_dual_shadow.py`\n\nLet me start with the three implementations. I'll write them one by one.\n\nFor the slippage buffer:\n- In `run_live_execution_v1.py`, the ref_price for buy signals comes from `ref_price = realtime_price if realtime_price > 0 else fallback_price` at around line 2067\n\n\n- I'll apply a 0.15% discount to buy prices to account for slippage\n\nFor the overfitting gate, I'm building a script that loads the strategy config, runs the backtest across multiple market regimes (2018-2019, 2020-2021, 2022-2023, 2024-2025), and checks if annual returns stay positive and Sharpe ratios above 0.5 in at least three of those four periods.\n\nFor the shadow upgrade threshold, I'm adding logic to the dual shadow system that requires a minimum of 20 trading days and a Sharpe ratio above 1.0, writing the upgrade eligibility status to the live payload JSON.\n\nStarting with the slippage buffer in the live execution module where prices are determined.\n","thinkingSignature":"9efce6463c09e3692bcf5480f46be77773b18409772c467c1acd2ffdc6cc1bc6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zgy64mdlf2mx_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '2060,2125p' /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_live_execution_v1.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1672,"output":371,"cacheRead":141248,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":143291,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timesta