{"type":"message","id":"2fd771f9","parentId":"dac18e41","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:37:10.658Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_amq0loj65jl4_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"def build_shadow_live_payload(\n    *,\n    baseline_payload: dict[str, Any],\n    baseline_curve_path: Path,\n    baseline_metrics: dict[str, Any],\n    selected_snapshot: dict[str, Any],\n    shadow_curve_path: Path,\n    summary_path: Path,\n) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    payload = copy.deepcopy(baseline_payload)\n    payload[\"dual_factor_overlay\"] = {\n        \"mode\": \"shadow_only\",\n        \"status\": \"candidate_for_paper_shadow\",\n        \"baseline_combo_v1\": baseline_payload.get(\"combo_v1\", {}),\n        \"baseline_metrics_normalized\": baseline_metrics,\n        \"selected_profile\": selected_snapshot[\"profile\"],\n        \"selected_metrics\": selected_snapshot[\"metrics\"],\n        \"selected_diff_vs_baseline\": selected_snapshot[\"diff_vs_baseline\"],\n        \"selected_params\": selected_snapshot[\"params\"],\n        \"latest_state\": selected_snapshot[\"latest_state\"],\n        \"runtime_shadow_inputs\": selected_snapshot[\"runtime_shadow_inputs\"],\n        \"guardrails\": [\n            \"不直接覆盖 combo_v1，先作为 shadow overlay 并行落地。\",\n            \"纸盘阶段先比对 runtime gate 与 orders diff，未完成对照前不替换主链路。\",\n            \"出现 dual 指标异常或数据不新鲜时，立即回退到 baseline combo_v1。\",\n        ],\n        \"files\": {\n            \"baseline_curve\": str(baseline_curve_path),\n            \"shadow_curve\": str(shadow_curve_path),\n            \"shadow_summary\": str(summary_path),\n        },\n    }\n    return payload\n\n\ndef main() -> None:\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description=\"构建 live_system_v1 的双因子正式集成 shadow 产物\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--live-json\", default=\"\", help=\"指定 live_system_v1_YYYYMMDD.json；默认自动取最新\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--formal-params\", default=str(FORMAL_PARAMS_PATH), help=\"formal params json\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--robustness\", default=str(ROBUSTNESS_PATH), help=\"robustness json\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--sse-index-file\", default=str(DEFAULT_SSE_INDEX_FILE), help=\"上证综指缓存 csv\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--profile\", choices=[\"default\", \"conservative\"], default=\"default\", help=\"选定输出 profile\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--write-artifacts\", action=\"store_true\", help=\"写出 shadow 曲线/摘要/live payload\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--output-prefix\", default=\"dual_factor_shadow\", help=\"输出前缀，仅在 --write-artifacts 时生效\")\n    args = parser.parse_args()\n\n    live_json_path = Path(args.live_json).expanduser().resolve() if args.live_json else discover_latest_live_json()\n    formal_params_path = Path(args.formal_params).expanduser().resolve()\n    robustness_path = Path(args.robustness).expanduser().resolve()\n    sse_index_file = Path(args.sse_index_file).expanduser().resolve()\n\n    formal_params = load_json(formal_params_path) if formal_params_path.exists() else None\n    robustness = load_json(robustness_path) if robustness_path.exists() else None\n    profiles = build_profiles(formal_params)\n\n    live_payload, baseline_curve_path, baseline_curve = load_live_payload(live_json_path)\n    baseline_metrics = normalize_metrics(baseline_curve)\n    market_close = load_market_close(baseline_curve.index)\n    sse_index = load_sse_index(baseline_curve.index, sse_index_file)\n\n    snapshots: dict[str, dict[str, Any]] = {}\n    curve_frames: dict[str, pd.DataFrame] = {}\n    for profile_name, profile in profiles.items():"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":245,"aggregated":"def build_shadow_live_payload(\n    *,\n    baseline_payload: dict[str, Any],\n    baseline_curve_path: Path,\n    baseline_metrics: dict[str, Any],\n    selected_snapshot: dict[str, Any],\n    shadow_curve_path: Path,\n    summary_path: Path,\n) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    payload = copy.deepcopy(baseline_payload)\n    payload[\"dual_factor_overlay\"] = {\n        \"mode\": \"shadow_only\",\n        \"status\": \"candidate_for_paper_shadow\",\n        \"baseline_combo_v1\": baseline_payload.get(\"combo_v1\", {}),\n        \"baseline_metrics_normalized\": baseline_metrics,\n        \"selected_profile\": selected_snapshot[\"profile\"],\n        \"selected_metrics\": selected_snapshot[\"metrics\"],\n        \"selected_diff_vs_baseline\": selected_snapshot[\"diff_vs_baseline\"],\n        \"selected_params\": selected_snapshot[\"params\"],\n        \"latest_state\": selected_snapshot[\"latest_state\"],\n        \"runtime_shadow_inputs\": selected_snapshot[\"runtime_shadow_inputs\"],\n        \"guardrails\": [\n            \"不直接覆盖 combo_v1，先作为 shadow overlay 并行落地。\",\n            \"纸盘阶段先比对 runtime gate 与 orders diff，未完成对照前不替换主链路。\",\n            \"出现 dual 指标异常或数据不新鲜时，立即回退到 baseline combo_v1。\",\n        ],\n        \"files\": {\n            \"baseline_curve\": str(baseline_curve_path),\n            \"shadow_curve\": str(shadow_curve_path),\n            \"shadow_summary\": str(summary_path),\n        },\n    }\n    return payload\n\n\ndef main() -> None:\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description=\"构建 live_system_v1 的双因子正式集成 shadow 产物\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--live-json\", default=\"\", help=\"指定 live_system_v1_YYYYMMDD.json；默认自动取最新\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--formal-params\", default=str(FORMAL_PARAMS_PATH), help=\"formal params json\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--robustness\", default=str(ROBUSTNESS_PATH), help=\"robustness json\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--sse-index-file\", default=str(DEFAULT_SSE_INDEX_FILE), help=\"上证综指缓存 csv\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--profile\", choices=[\"default\", \"conservative\"], default=\"default\", help=\"选定输出 profile\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--write-artifacts\", action=\"store_true\", help=\"写出 shadow 曲线/摘要/live payload\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--output-prefix\", default=\"dual_factor_shadow\", help=\"输出前缀，仅在 --write-artifacts 时生效\")\n    args = parser.parse_args()\n\n    live_json_path = Path(args.live_json).expanduser().resolve() if args.live_json else discover_latest_live_json()\n    formal_params_path = Path(args.formal_params).expanduser().resolve()\n    robustness_path = Path(args.robustness).expanduser().resolve()\n    sse_index_file = Path(args.sse_index_file).expanduser().resolve()\n\n    formal_params = load_json(formal_params_path) if formal_params_path.exists() else None\n    robustness = load_json(robustness_path) if robustness_path.exists() else None\n    profiles = build_profiles(formal_params)\n\n    live_payload, baseline_curve_path, baseline_curve = load_live_payload(live_json_path)\n    baseline_metrics = normalize_metrics(baseline_curve)\n    market_close = load_market_close(baseline_curve.index)\n    sse_index = load_sse_index(baseline_curve.index, sse_index_file)\n\n    snapshots: dict[str, dict[str, Any]] = {}\n    curve_frames: dict[str, pd.DataFrame] = {}\n    for profile_name, profile in profiles.items():","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776155830587}}
{"type":"message","id":"640167f5","parentId":"2fd771f9","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:37:34.484Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the structure. I need to:\n1. Add an OOS stress test (2018-2022) to `integrate_dual_factor_overlay.py` as part of the shadow pipeline\n2. Add `min_shadow_days`, `oos_sharpe`, `oos_ann_ret`, `oos_mdd` to the live_payload\n3. In `run_live_system_v1_dual_shadow.py`, add an upgrade gate check\n\nBut this is getting complex. Let me think about the right approach.\n\nThe `integrate_dual_factor_overlay.py` currently:\n- Takes a live_system_v1 JSON (which contains the recent backtest curve)\n\n\n- Computes the dual factor overlay metrics against that curve\n- Outputs a shadow payload\n\nBut the OOS stress test (2018-2022) would need the full historical backtest data. Looking at the `strict_oos_aggressive_report`, it already does this kind of validation for the breadth strategy. For the dual factor overlay, I should add OOS validation as part of the shadow pipeline, computing the dual factor metrics over the cold period 2018-2022.\n\nRather than building a full parameter selection framework like the existing OOS system, I can apply a simpler approach: take the current dual factor params, run them over 2018-2022 to get OOS metrics, and if those metrics fail the gate (negative returns, Sharpe below threshold, or max drawdown exceeding limits), reject the shadow from upgrading to gray. The most pragmatic place to implement this is within `integrate_dual_factor_overlay.py` itself, where I can add an OOS validation step that generates the necessary metrics for the upgrade gate decision.\n\nTo run this validation, I need the historical benchmark curve data for 2018-2022, which should already be available in the existing backtest files. The validation would compute metrics like annualized return and Sharpe ratio on the out-of-sample period, then add these as `oos_metrics` to the payload with a simple pass/fail gate based on whether returns are positive and Sharpe exceeds 0.5.\n\nFor the shadow upgrade threshold, I need to ensure both conditions are met: at least 20 shadow days have elapsed and the OOS Sharpe ratio is greater than 1.0 before allowing the upgrade. The shadow days counter should already be tracked in the payload, so I just need to verify it's being recorded correctly.","thinkingSignature":"461d6d37a5fcc60269c564611d4a8ae9e462e9de5ce8a8908483d2919ccc1d13"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2hknfw5m9xhp_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/dual_factor_shadow_20260414_conservative_20260414_live_payload.json 2>/dev/null | python3 -c \"\nimport json, sys\nd = json.load(sys.stdin)\ndf = d.get('dual_factor_overlay', {})\nprint('=== selected_metrics ===')\nprint(json.dumps(df.get('selected_metrics', {}), indent=2))\nprint()\nprint('=== latest_state ===')\nprint(json.dumps(df.get('latest_state', {}), indent=2))\nprint()\nprint('=== runtime_shadow_inputs ===')\nprint(json.dumps(df.get('runtime_shadow_inputs', {}), indent=2))\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":38998,"output":676,"cacheRead":35567,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75241,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776155830667,"responseId":"062d2fb936129ae3e9dab4928fbbb931"}}
