{"type":"message","id":"18867070","parentId":"b81c221a","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:40:08.312Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so the existing backtest runs from 2024-2026, not 2018-2022. For the 过拟合压力测试, I'll need a different approach.Let me think about what actually matters here:\n\n1. **参数脆弱性测试 (Param Fragility Test)** — from the article: \"把动量回溯天数从 25 天改成 20 天，年化从 78% 跌到 31%。\" This tests if the strategy is overfitted to specific parameter values.\n\n2. **冷区间 OOS 测试** — run the strategy on 2018-2022 data where the market was very different (trade war, COVID crash, etc.)\n   \nThe conservative profile parameters (ROC10 bull/bear=1.10/0.90, RSV5 bull/bear=1.05/0.95) are already more resilient than the default ones, so the real question is whether they can hold up across different market regimes. The challenge is that running a full OOS backtest on 2018-2022 requires the complete dual factor pipeline, which is complex. Instead, I could do something simpler: apply the conservative multiplier series to the existing live period data and compare how the strategy performs under different parameter regimes.\n\nActually, I should just implement a straightforward stress test framework in `integrate_dual_factor_overlay.py`. I'll create functions to perturb the key parameters (bull/bear multipliers for both ROC10 and RSV5), compute the strategy under each scenario, and measure how much returns degrade. This is exactly what the article suggests and it gives a direct sense of whether the strategy's performance is fragile to parameter changes.\n\nBut wait—there's a chicken-and-egg problem here. The stress test needs to run after parameters are selected, yet it should inform whether the strategy is overfitted. Let me think through this differently: I should add the stress test results to the shadow payload, and then use those results as a gate in the upgrade check. If the strategy fails the stress test, it can't upgrade from shadow to production.\n\nSo the real implementation needs three pieces: a stress test function that perturbs parameters and measures fragility, the upgrade gate logic that checks both the OOS Sharpe threshold and stress test results, and tracking of how many cumulative trading days the shadow period has accumulated.\n\nFor the stress test itself, I'll perturb the ROC10 bull threshold across a range like 1.05 to 1.20 and measure how much the Sharpe ratio degrades in each scenario—if it drops more than 50%, that's a sign of fragility. Now I need to write out the implementation script to tie this together.","thinkingSignature":"1f46d1b4ab9a762c8603ba2237f92a3a1fdd397595c489bf960de0d28da180d2"},{"type":"text","text":"现在写**过拟合压力测试**函数，加入 dual factor 影子链路：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ao38oi29agtl_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '1,30p' /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/integrate_dual_factor_overlay.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":46873,"output":617,"cacheRead":35567,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83057,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776155982110,"responseId":"062d30504f7ec839f644916a7ad748a4"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a8d5113e","parentId":"18867070","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:40:08.420Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ao38oi29agtl_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport argparse\nimport copy\nimport json\nimport re\nimport sys\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nimport pandas as pd\n\nPROJECT_ROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[1]\nREPORT_DIR = PROJECT_ROOT / \"research\" / \"reports\"\nFORMAL_PARAMS_PATH = REPORT_DIR / \"dual_factor_formal_params.json\"\nROBUSTNESS_PATH = REPORT_DIR / \"dual_factor_robustness_report.json\"\nDEFAULT_SSE_INDEX_FILE = Path(\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis/index_000001_SH.csv\")\n\nfor candidate in [PROJECT_ROOT, PROJECT_ROOT / \"scripts\"]:\n    if str(candidate) not in sys.path:\n        sys.path.insert(0, str(candidate))\n\nimport numpy as np  # noqa: E402\nimport run_strategy_695_batch as batch  # noqa: E402\n\nPROFILE_DEFAULT = {\n    \"name\": \"default\",\n    \"roc10\": {\"window\": 10, \"bull\": 1.15, \"bear\": 0.85},"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":29,"aggregated":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport argparse\nimport copy\nimport json\nimport re\nimport sys\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nimport pandas as pd\n\nPROJECT_ROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[1]\nREPORT_DIR = PROJECT_ROOT / \"research\" / \"reports\"\nFORMAL_PARAMS_PATH = REPORT_DIR / \"dual_factor_formal_params.json\"\nROBUSTNESS_PATH = REPORT_DIR / \"dual_factor_robustness_report.json\"\nDEFAULT_SSE_INDEX_FILE = Path(\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis/index_000001_SH.csv\")\n\nfor candidate in [PROJECT_ROOT, PROJECT_ROOT / \"scripts\"]:\n    if str(candidate) not in sys.path:\n        sys.path.insert(0, str(candidate))\n\nimport numpy as np  # noqa: E402\nimport run_strategy_695_batch as batch  # noqa: E402\n\nPROFILE_DEFAULT = {\n    \"name\": \"default\",\n    \"roc10\": {\"window\": 10, \"bull\": 1.15, \"bear\": 0.85},","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776156008409}}
{"type":"message","id":"def7b062","parentId":"a8d5113e","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:40:18.934Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to add the stress test function and the OOS gate. Let me write the code.\n\nThe stress test will:\n1. Perturb key params (bull/bear multipliers for ROC10 and RSV5)\n2. Check if the strategy is robust (returns don't drop >50% under perturbed params)\n\nThe OOS gate will:\n1. Track shadow days in a state file\n2. Check `shadow_days >= 20 AND oos_ann_ret > 0 AND oos_sharpe > 1.0` before setting upgrade_eligible=true\n\nLet me now add the stress test to integrate_dual_factor_overlay.py and the upgrade gate to run_live_system_v1_dual_shadow.py.\n\n\nI should first examine the full structure of run_live_system_v1_dual_shadow.py to understand how to properly integrate these changes.","thinkingSignature":"edbeb85da72521cffab19cd885fe60cc95187f0efb0c4fc6028fc63812a5c798"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xuhyfga2iopk_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '150,260p' /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_live_system_v1_dual_shadow.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":47749,"output":241,"cacheRead":35567,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83557,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776156008424,"responseId":"062d306c312819a7282b932482b07fdc"}}
{"type":"message","id":"98567cd5","parentId":"def7b062","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:40:19.077Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_xuhyfga2iopk_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"latest_state\": selected.get(\"latest_state\", {}),\n        \"guardrails\": guardrails,\n    }\n\n\ndef main() -> None:\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(\n        description=\"Dual Factor Feature Flag Wrapper — 读取 live_system_v1 结果并叠加 dual factor shadow\",\n    )\n    parser.add_argument(\n        \"--profile\",\n        choices=[\"off\", \"default\", \"conservative\"],\n        default=\"off\",\n        help=(\n            \"off=不叠加（纯 baseline），\"\n            \"conservative=保守档 dual factor（放大/收缩幅度 ±5%%~±10%%），\"\n            \"default=正式候选档 dual factor（放大/收缩幅度 ±10%%~±15%%）。\"\n            \"off 为主链路默认值。\"\n        ),\n    )\n    parser.add_argument(\n        \"--live-json\",\n        default=\"\",\n        help=\"指定 live_system_v1_YYYYMMDD.json；默认自动取最新\",\n    )\n    parser.add_argument(\n        \"--write-artifacts\",\n        action=\"store_true\",\n        help=\"写出 shadow 曲线/摘要/live payload（默认只打印摘要，不写文件）\",\n    )\n    parser.add_argument(\n        \"--dry-run\",\n        action=\"store_true\",\n        help=\"仅打印 diff 对照，不写任何文件\",\n    )\n    parser.add_argument(\n        \"--output-prefix\",\n        default=\"dual_factor_shadow\",\n        help=\"输出前缀（仅 --write-artifacts 时生效）\",\n    )\n    args = parser.parse_args()\n\n    # ---- 解析 profile ----\n    profile = args.profile.lower().strip()\n    if profile not in VALID_PROFILES:\n        raise ValueError(f\"无效 profile={profile}，合法值：{VALID_PROFILES}\")\n\n    # ---- 发现 baseline live_system_v1 ----\n    if args.live_json:\n        live_json_path = Path(args.live_json).expanduser().resolve()\n    else:\n        live_json_path = discover_latest_live_json()\n\n    if not live_json_path.exists():\n        raise FileNotFoundError(f\"live_system_v1 JSON 不存在：{live_json_path}，请先运行 run_live_system_v1.py\")\n\n    baseline_payload = json.loads(live_json_path.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\n    date_tag = str(baseline_payload.get(\"date\") or datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\"))\n    output_prefix = f\"{args.output_prefix}_{date_tag}\"\n\n    # ---- 处理三种模式 ----\n    result: dict[str, Any] = {\n        \"generated_at\": datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\"),\n        \"feature_flag\": {\n            \"field\": \"dual_factor_profile\",\n            \"profile\": profile,\n            \"valid_values\": list(VALID_PROFILES),\n            \"main_line_unchanged\": profile == \"off\",\n        },\n        \"live_system_v1\": str(live_json_path),\n        \"date_tag\": date_tag,\n    }\n\n    if profile == \"off\":\n        # off 模式：不做任何 dual factor 叠加\n        result[\"status\"] = \"off\"\n        result[\"message\"] = \"dual_factor_profile=off，未做任何 dual factor 叠加，baseline combo_v1 保持不变\"\n        result[\"baseline_metrics\"] = baseline_payload.get(\"combo_v1\", {})\n        result[\"shadow\"] = None\n        print(json.dumps(result, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\n        return\n\n    # ---- default / conservative：调用 integrate_dual_factor_overlay ----\n    shadow_summary = run_dual_shadow(\n        live_json_path=live_json_path,\n        profile=profile,\n        write_artifacts=(args.write_artifacts and not args.dry_run),\n        output_prefix=output_prefix,\n    )\n\n    diff = build_shadow_diff_summary(\n        baseline_payload=baseline_payload,\n        shadow_summary=shadow_summary,\n        profile=profile,\n    )\n\n    result[\"status\"] = \"shadow_generated\"\n    result[\"profile\"] = profile\n    result[\"feature_flag_note\"] = (\n        \"shadow 产物已生成，但 baseline combo_v1 仍未被替换；\"\n        \"需在完成 shadow 对照验证后，通过 feature flag 切换才可正式接入主链路\"\n    )\n    result[\"shadow\"] = diff\n    result[\"shadow_summary\"] = shadow_summary\n\n    if args.dry_run:\n        result[\"artifacts_written\"] = False\n        result[\"message\"] = \"dry-run 模式，仅打印 shadow diff，不写文件\"\n    else:\n        result[\"artifacts_written\"] = args.write_artifacts\n        result[\"message\"] = ("}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":26,"aggregated":"\"latest_state\": selected.get(\"latest_state\", {}),\n        \"guardrails\": guardrails,\n    }\n\n\ndef main() -> None:\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(\n        description=\"Dual Factor Feature Flag Wrapper — 读取 live_system_v1 结果并叠加 dual factor shadow\",\n    )\n    parser.add_argument(\n        \"--profile\",\n        choices=[\"off\", \"default\", \"conservative\"],\n        default=\"off\",\n        help=(\n            \"off=不叠加（纯 baseline），\"\n            \"conservative=保守档 dual factor（放大/收缩幅度 ±5%%~±10%%），\"\n            \"default=正式候选档 dual factor（放大/收缩幅度 ±10%%~±15%%）。\"\n            \"off 为主链路默认值。\"\n        ),\n    )\n    parser.add_argument(\n        \"--live-json\",\n        default=\"\",\n        help=\"指定 live_system_v1_YYYYMMDD.json；默认自动取最新\",\n    )\n    parser.add_argument(\n        \"--write-artifacts\",\n        action=\"store_true\",\n        help=\"写出 shadow 曲线/摘要/live payload（默认只打印摘要，不写文件）\",\n    )\n    parser.add_argument(\n        \"--dry-run\",\n        action=\"store_true\",\n        help=\"仅打印 diff 对照，不写任何文件\",\n    )\n    parser.add_argument(\n        \"--output-prefix\",\n        default=\"dual_factor_shadow\",\n        help=\"输出前缀（仅 --write-artifacts 时生效）\",\n    )\n    args = parser.parse_args()\n\n    # ---- 解析 profile ----\n    profile = args.profile.lower().strip()\n    if profile not in VALID_PROFILES:\n        raise ValueError(f\"无效 profile={profile}，合法值：{VALID_PROFILES}\")\n\n    # ---- 发现 baseline live_system_v1 ----\n    if args.live_json:\n        live_json_path = Path(args.live_json).expanduser().resolve()\n    else:\n        live_json_path = discover_latest_live_json()\n\n    if not live_json_path.exists():\n        raise FileNotFoundError(f\"live_system_v1 JSON 不存在：{live_json_path}，请先运行 run_live_system_v1.py\")\n\n    baseline_payload = json.loads(live_json_path.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\n    date_tag = str(baseline_payload.get(\"date\") or datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\"))\n    output_prefix = f\"{args.output_prefix}_{date_tag}\"\n\n    # ---- 处理三种模式 ----\n    result: dict[str, Any] = {\n        \"generated_at\": datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\"),\n        \"feature_flag\": {\n            \"field\": \"dual_factor_profile\",\n            \"profile\": profile,\n            \"valid_values\": list(VALID_PROFILES),\n            \"main_line_unchanged\": profile == \"off\",\n        },\n        \"live_system_v1\": str(live_json_path),\n        \"date_tag\": date_tag,\n    }\n\n    if profile == \"off\":\n        # off 模式：不做任何 dual factor 叠加\n        result[\"status\"] = \"off\"\n        result[\"message\"] = \"dual_factor_profile=off，未做任何 dual factor 叠加，baseline combo_v1 保持不变\"\n        result[\"baseline_metrics\"] = baseline_payload.get(\"combo_v1\", {})\n        result[\"shadow\"] = None\n        print(json.dumps(result, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\n        return\n\n    # ---- default / conservative：调用 integrate_dual_factor_overlay ----\n    shadow_summary = run_dual_shadow(\n        live_json_path=live_json_path,\n        profile=profile,\n        write_artifacts=(args.write_artifacts and not args.dry_run),\n        output_prefix=output_prefix,\n    )\n\n    diff = build_shadow_diff_summary(\n        baseline_payload=baseline_payload,\n        shadow_summary=shadow_summary,\n        profile=profile,\n    )\n\n    result[\"status\"] = \"shadow_generated\"\n    result[\"profile\"] = profile\n    result[\"feature_flag_note\"] = (\n        \"shadow 产物已生成，但 baseline combo_v1 仍未被替换；\"\n        \"需在完成 shadow 对照验证后，通过 feature flag 切换才可正式接入主链路\"\n    )\n    result[\"shadow\"] = diff\n    result[\"shadow_summary\"] = shadow_summary\n\n    if args.dry_run:\n        result[\"artifacts_written\"] = False\n        result[\"message\"] = \"dry-run 模式，仅打印 shadow diff，不写文件\"\n    else:\n        result[\"artifacts_written\"] = args.write_artifacts\n        result[\"message\"] = (","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776156019061}}
{"type":"message","id":"8da1eac6","parentId":"98567cd5","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:42:13.238Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the structure. Let me create the plan:\n\n1. **`integrate_dual_factor_overlay.py`**: Add `stress_test_params()` function and OOS validation. This will compute stress metrics and add them to the shadow payload.\n\n2. **`run_live_system_v1_dual_shadow.py`**: Add `shadow_upgrade_gate()` function that:   - Tracks shadow cumulative days   - Checks OOS metrics\n   - Sets `upgrade_eligible` flag\n\nLet me now write the implementation. I'll add a stress test function in `integrate_dual_factor_overlay.py`.The stress test will use the conservative profile params and run a simplified version of the dual factor overlay on the existing curve data. \n\nI'll perturb the key parameters—adjusting bull thresholds up and down by 0.05 while moving bear thresholds by the same amount—and measure how much the annualized return drops relative to the baseline scenario. If the decline exceeds 30%, the strategy is considered fragile. For the OOS validation, I can leverage the `backtest_dual_factor_overlay.py` with a date range filter to isolate 2018-2022 performance.\n\nThe cleanest path forward is to add the stress test directly to `integrate_dual_factor_overlay.py` since it already has access to the conservative profile parameters and curve data. I'll compute both the baseline and perturbed Sharpe ratios using the same conservative multiplier approach, then calculate how much performance degrades under each scenario.\n\nAdding stress test function...","thinkingSignature":"efc929f2511377f01add59594e7b11f5cde7ddd25a50bc52eef530bf4b03ae4d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_du4qlrtrahc2_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n过拟合压力测试 + OOS冷区间验证 — 双因子影子链路专用\n\n文章「回测美如画，shi pan亏成狗」的四个坑:\n  1. 未来函数      → 每次调参跑 AI 代码扫描（已有人工习惯，保持）\n  2. 过拟合        → 参数脆弱性测试（本文）: 改动关键参数后验证稳定性\n  3. 三个数字不够  → 年度拆解 + 月度热力图（已有 generate_strategy_performance_panel.py）\n  4. 滑点积累      → 已在 run_live_execution_v1.py 加 SLIPPAGE_BP=15 buffer\n\n本模块实现第2项：对保守参数做参数脆弱性压力测试，\n类似文章中\"把止损线从8%改成10%\"，\"把动量回溯天数从25天改成20天\"的验证方式。\n\"\"\"\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport json\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nimport numpy as np\nimport pandas as pd\n\nPROJECT_ROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[1]\nREPORT_DIR = PROJECT_ROOT / \"research\" / \"reports\"\nDEFAULT_SSE_INDEX_FILE = Path(\n    \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis/index_000001_SH.csv\"\n)\n\nfor candidate in [PROJECT_ROOT, PROJECT_ROOT / \"scripts\"]:\n    if str(candidate) not in __import__(\"sys\").path:\n        __import__(\"sys\").path.insert(0, str(candidate))\n\nimport run_strategy_695_batch as batch  # noqa: E402\n\n\ndef load_curve(curve_path: Path) -> pd.Series:\n    \"\"\"Load daily return series from a curve CSV.\"\"\"\n    df = pd.read_csv(curve_path)\n    if \"date\" not in df.columns or \"daily_return\" not in df.columns:\n        raise ValueError(f\"curve file missing required columns: {curve_path}\")\n    df = df.copy()\n    df[\"date\"] = pd.to_datetime(df[\"date\"], errors=\"coerce\")\n    df[\"daily_return\"] = pd.to_numeric(df[\"daily_return\"], errors=\"coerce\")\n    df = df.dropna(subset=[\"date\", \"daily_return\"]).sort_values(\"date\")\n    return df.set_index(\"date\")[\"daily_return\"].astype(float)\n\n\ndef calc_metrics(series: pd.Series) -> dict[str, float]:\n    \"\"\"Compute ann_ret, max_dd, sharpe from a daily return series.\"\"\"\n    clean = series.dropna().astype(float)\n    if len(clean) == 0:\n        return {\"ann_ret\": 0.0, \"max_dd\": 0.0, \"sharpe\": 0.0, \"n\": 0}\n    nav = (1 + clean).cumprod()\n    total = nav.iloc[-1] / nav.iloc[0] - 1\n    ann = (1 + total) ** (252.0 / len(clean)) - 1\n    max_dd = abs((nav / nav.cummax() - 1).min())\n    vol = clean.std() * np.sqrt(252.0)\n    sharpe = (clean.mean() * 252.0) / vol if vol > 0 else 0.0\n    return {\n        \"ann_ret\": round(float(ann * 100), 2),\n        \"max_dd\": round(float(max_dd * 100), 2),\n        \"sharpe\": round(float(sharpe), 3),\n        \"n\": int(len(clean)),\n    }\n\n\ndef build_roc10_multiplier(\n    index: pd.DatetimeIndex,\n    *,\n    window: int = 10,\n    bull: float = 1.10,\n    bear: float = 0.90,\n) -> pd.Series:\n    \"\"\"Build ROC10-based regime multiplier series for the given index.\"\"\"\n    market_close = batch.load_market_matrices(max_symbols=180)[0].mean(axis=1, skipna=True)\n    market_close.index = pd.to_datetime(market_close.index)\n    roc = market_close.reindex(index).ffill().bfill().pct_change(window)\n    mult = pd.Series(1.0, index=index)\n    mult[roc > 0] = bull\n    mult[roc <= 0] = bear\n    return mult\n\n\ndef build_rsv5_multiplier(\n    index: pd.DatetimeIndex,\n    *,\n    window: int = 5,\n    median_window: int = 60,\n    bull: float = 1.05,\n    bear: float = 0.95,\n    sse_index_file: Path | None = None,\n) -> pd.Series:\n    \"\"\"Build RSV5-based regime multiplier series using SSE index OHLC.\"\"\"\n    sse = sse_index_file or DEFAULT_SSE_INDEX_FILE\n    if not sse.exists():\n        raise FileNotFoundError(f\"SSE index cache not found: {sse}\")\n\n    idx = pd.read_csv(sse)\n    idx = idx.copy()\n    idx[\"date\"] = pd.to_datetime(idx[\"trade_date\"].astype(str), format=\"%Y%m%d\", errors=\"coerce\")\n    idx = idx.dropna(subset=[\"date\"]).sort_values(\"date\").set_index(\"date\")\n    close = pd.to_numeric(idx[\"close\"], errors=\"coerce\")\n    high = pd.to_numeric(idx[\"high\"], errors=\"coerce\")\n    low = pd.to_numeric(idx[\"low\"], errors=\"coerce\")\n    rolling_low = low.rolling(window, min_periods=1).min()\n    rolling_high = high.rolling(window, min_periods=1).max()\n    rsv = (close - rolling_low) / (rolling_high - rolling_low + 1e-9)\n    rsv = rsv.reindex(index).ffill().bfill()\n    median = rsv.rolling(median_window, min_periods=20).median().ffill().bfill()\n    mult = pd.Series(1.0, index=index)\n    mult[rsv > median] = bull\n    mult[rsv <= median] = bear\n    return mult\n\n\ndef apply_dual_overlay(\n    returns: pd.Series,\n    roc10_mult: pd.Series,\n    rsv5_mult: pd.Series,\n) -> pd.Series:\n    \"\"\"Apply dual regime overlay to returns (conservative profile: multiply both multipliers).\"\"\"\n    aligned = returns.reindex(roc10_mult.index).ffill().bfill().fillna(0)\n    dual = roc10_mult.reindex(aligned.index).ffill().fillna(1.0) * rsv5_mult.reindex(aligned.index).ffill().fillna(1.0)\n    return aligned * dual\n\n\n# — 保守参数（与 integrate_dual_factor_overlay.py 保持一致）—\nCONSERVATIVE_PARAMS = {\n    \"roc10\": {\"window\": 10, \"bull\": 1.10, \"bear\": 0.90},\n    \"rsv5\": {\"window\": 5, \"median_window\": 60, \"bull\": 1.05, \"bear\": 0.95},\n}\n\n# — 压力测试参数扰动表（来自文章经验：±5pp 的扰动就能暴露过拟合）—\nSTRESS_SCENARIOS = [\n    # (label, roc10_bull_Δ, roc10_bear_Δ, rsv5_bull_Δ, rsv5_bear_Δ)\n    (\"ROC10_bull-0.10\", -0.10, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00),  # ROC10 bull 从 1.10 → 1.00\n    (\"ROC10_bull+0.10\", +0.10, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00),  # ROC10 bull 从 1.10 → 1.20\n    (\"ROC10_bear+0.10\", 0.00, +0.10, 0.00, 0.00),  # ROC10 bear 从 0.90 → 1.00（缩小利差）\n    (\"RSV5_bull-0.10\", 0.00, 0.00, -0.10, 0.00),  # RSV5 bull 从 1.05 → 0.95\n    (\"RSV5_bull+0.10\", 0.00, 0.00, +0.10, 0.00),  # RSV5 bull 从 1.05 → 1.15\n    (\"all_tighter\", -0.10, +0.10, -0.10, +0.10),  # 所有 multiplier 收紧 → 最严苛场景\n    (\"all_looser\", +0.10, -0.10, +0.10, -0.10),  # 所有 multiplier 放宽\n]\n\n\ndef run_stress_test(curve_path: Path) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    \"\"\"\n    运行参数脆弱性压力测试。\n\n    流程：\n    1. 加载基准曲线（full period, 2024-现在）\n    2. 用保守参数计算基准 dual overlay 收益\n    3. 对每个扰动场景重新计算\n    4. 检查每个场景下 ann_ret 下降是否 < 50%（文章经验：超过即脆弱）\n\n    返回 stress_test 结果字典。\n    \"\"\"\n    result: dict[str, Any] = {\n        \"status\": \"pass\",\n        \"pass\": True,\n        \"scenarios\": [],\n        \"fragility_score\": 0.0,  # 0=完全稳定，1=完全脆弱\n        \"worst_case_ret_drop_pp\": 0.0,\n    }\n\n    try:\n        returns = load_curve(curve_path)\n    except Exception as e:\n        return {\"status\": \"error\", \"pass\": False, \"reason\": str(e)}\n\n    # — 基准保守参数 overlay —\n    p = CONSERVATIVE_PARAMS\n    try:\n        idx = returns.index\n        roc10 = build_roc10_multiplier(idx, **p[\"roc10\"])\n        rsv5 = build_rsv5_multiplier(idx, **p[\"rsv5\"])\n        base_dual = apply_dual_overlay(returns, roc10, rsv5)\n        base_metrics = calc_metrics(base_dual)\n    except Exception as e:\n        return {\"status\": \"error\", \"pass\": False, \"reason\": f\"baseline overlay failed: {e}\"}\n\n    base_ann_ret = base_metrics[\"ann_ret\"]\n\n    # — 遍历每个扰动场景 —\n    worst_ret = base_ann_ret\n    for label, db, eb, ds, es in STRESS_SCENARIOS:\n        scen_params = {\n            \"roc10\": {**p[\"roc10\"], \"bull\": p[\"roc10\"][\"bull\"] + db, \"bear\": p[\"roc10\"][\"bear\"] + eb},\n            \"rsv5\": {**p[\"rsv5\"], \"bull\": p[\"rsv5\"][\"bull\"] + ds, \"bear\": p[\"rsv5\"][\"bear\"] + es},\n        }\n        # 确保 bull > bear（逻辑约束）\n        if scen_params[\"roc10\"][\"bull\"] <= scen_params[\"roc10\"][\"bear\"]:\n            continue\n        if scen_params[\"rsv5\"][\"bull\"] <= scen_params[\"rsv5\"][\"bear\"]:\n            continue\n\n        try:\n            roc10_s = build_roc10_multiplier(idx, **scen_params[\"roc10\"])\n            rsv5_s = build_rsv5_multiplier(idx, **scen_params[\"rsv5\"])\n            scen_dual = apply_dual_overlay(returns, roc10_s, rsv5_s)\n            scen_metrics = calc_metrics(scen_dual)\n        except Exception:\n            continue\n\n        ret_drop = base_ann_ret - scen_metrics[\"ann_ret\"]  # 正数 = 性能下降\n        worst_ret = min(worst_ret, scen_metrics[\"ann_ret\"])\n\n        # 脆弱判定：ann_ret 下降 > 15pp（保守阈值，比文章更严）\n        is_fragile = ret_drop > 15.0\n        if is_fragile:\n            result[\"pass\"] = False\n            result[\"status\"] = \"fragile\"\n\n        result[\"scenarios\"].append({\n            \"label\": label,\n            \"ann_ret\": scen_metrics[\"ann_ret\"],\n            \"sharpe\": scen_metrics[\"sharpe\"],\n            \"max_dd\": scen_metrics[\"max_dd\"],\n            \"ret_drop_pp\": round(ret_drop, 2),\n            \"fragile\": is_fragile,\n        })\n\n    result[\"baseline_ann_ret\"] = base_ann_ret\n    result[\"baseline_sharpe\"] = base_metrics[\"sharpe\"]\n    result[\"worst_case_ret_drop_pp\"] = round(base_ann_ret - worst_ret, 2)\n    result[\"fragility_score\"] = round(\n        max(0.0, min(1.0, result[\"worst_case_ret_drop_pp\"] / 30.0)), 3\n    )  # 30pp → 1.0 score\n\n    return result\n\n\n# — OOS 冷区间验证 —\nOOS_COLD_START = \"2018-01-02\"\nOOS_COLD_END = \"2022-12-30\"\n\n\ndef run_oos_cold_test(curve_path: Path) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    \"\"\"\n    OOS 冷区间验证：在 2018-2022（贸易战 + COVID + 震荡市）验证双因子表现。\n\n    文章经验：\"把回测区间从 2023-2025 改成 2018-2022，完全跑不出正收益\"\n    → 如果在 2018-2022 依然有正收益且 Sharpe > 0.5，说明策略不过拟合\n    \"\"\"\n    result: dict[str, Any] = {\n        \"period\": f\"{OOS_COLD_START}~{OOS_COLD_END}\",\n        \"status\": \"unknown\",\n        \"ann_ret\": 0.0,\n        \"sharpe\": 0.0,\n        \"max_dd\": 0.0,\n        \"pass\": False,\n        \"reason\": \"\",\n    }\n\n    try:\n        returns = load_curve(curve_path)\n        # 限制到冷区间\n        cold = returns[\n            (returns.index >= pd.Timestamp(OOS_COLD_START))\n            & (returns.index <= pd.Timestamp(OOS_COLD_END))\n        ]\n        if len(cold) < 100:\n            result[\"status\"] = \"insufficient_data\"\n            result[\"reason\"] = f\"冷区间仅 {len(cold)} 个交易日（<100），跳过\"\n            return result\n    except Exception as e:\n        result[\"status\"] = \"error\"\n        result[\"reason\"] = str(e)\n        return result\n\n    p = CONSERVATIVE_PARAMS\n    try:\n        idx = cold.index\n        roc10 = build_roc10_multiplier(idx, **p[\"roc10\"])\n        rsv5 = build_rsv5_multiplier(idx, **p[\"rsv5\"])\n        dual_ret = apply_dual_overlay(cold, roc10, rsv5)\n        metrics = calc_metrics(dual_ret)\n    except FileNotFoundError as e:\n        result[\"status\"] = \"missing_data\"\n        result[\"reason\"] = f\"缺少市场数据（{OOS_COLD_START}~{OOS_COLD_END}），无法做冷区间验证\"\n        return result\n    except Exception as e:\n        result[\"status\"] = \"error\"\n        result[\"reason\"] = str(e)\n        return result\n\n    result[\"ann_ret\"] = metrics[\"ann_ret\"]\n    result[\"sharpe\"] = metrics[\"sharpe\"]\n    result[\"max_dd\"] = metrics[\"max_dd\"]\n    result[\"n\"] = metrics[\"n\"]\n    result[\"status\"] = \"computed\"\n\n    # Gate: ann_ret > 0 AND sharpe > 0.5（保守阈值，文章经验：0.5 作为底线）\n    if result[\"ann_ret\"] > 0 and result[\"sharpe\"] > 0.5:\n        result[\"pass\"] = True\n    elif result[\"ann_ret\"] <= 0:\n        result[\"pass\"] = False\n        result[\"reason\"] = f\"OOS ann_ret={result['ann_ret']}% <= 0，过拟合风险高\"\n    else:\n        result[\"pass\"] = False\n        result[\"reason\"] = f\"OOS Sharpe={result['sharpe']} <= 0.5（要求 >0.5），过拟合风险高\"\n\n    return result\n\n\ndef run_all_validation(curve_path: Path) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    \"\"\"运行全部两项验证（压力测试 + OOS 冷区间），合并结果。\"\"\"\n    stress = run_stress_test(curve_path)\n    oos = run_oos_cold_test(curve_path)\n\n    combined_pass = stress.get(\"pass\", False) and oos.get(\"pass\", False)\n\n    return {\n        \"status\": \"pass\" if combined_pass else \"fail\",\n        \"stress_test\": stress,\n        \"oos_cold_test\": oos,\n        \"upgrade_gate\": {\n            \"min_shadow_days\": 20,\n            \"oos_sharpe_min\": 1.0,\n            \"stress_pass_required\": True,\n            \"oos_pass_required\": True,\n        },\n        \"combined_pass\": combined_pass,\n        \"recommendation\": (\n            \"PASS — 可考虑 shadow→gray 升级\"\n            if combined_pass\n            else f\"FAIL — stress={'pass' if stress.get('pass') else 'FAIL'}, oos={'pass' if oos.get('pass') else 'FAIL'}\"\n        ),\n    }\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    import argparse\n\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description=\"双因子过拟合压力测试 + OOS 冷区间验证\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--curve\", default=\"\", help=\"曲线 CSV 路径，默认取最新 live_system_v1_combo_curve\")\n    args = parser.parse_args()\n\n    if args.curve:\n        curve_path = Path(args.curve)\n    else:\n        candidates = sorted(REPORT_DIR.glob(\"live_system_v1_combo_curve_????????.csv\"))\n        if not candidates:\n            print(\"未找到 live_system_v1_combo_curve_*.csv，先运行 run_live_system_v1.py 生成\")\n            exit(1)\n        curve_path = candidates[-1]\n\n    print(f\"Curve: {curve_path}\")\n    result = run_all_validation(curve_path)\n    print(json.dumps(result, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\n","path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/dual_factor_oos_stress_test.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":48957,"output":4334,"cacheRead":35567,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88858,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776156019081,"responseId":"062d308230e6204f5a847d98f3963da2"}}
