{"type":"message","id":"7fbbe734","parentId":"c16b4924","timestamp":"2026-04-14T10:34:58.895Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see there are actually 7 paper trading accounts (not 9):\n1. legacy_base\n2. defensive\n3. balanced\n4. aggressive\n5. exit_dual\n6. exit_tight\n7. alpha55\n\nBut the document says 7. Zhang Ling says 9. Maybe the breadth_aggressive is one, and maybe there's also the main combo_v1 live system... Let me check the trading metrics for each of these 7 types plus some others I found.\n\nActually wait - the document was from March 26. There might be more now. Let me also look at what \"量化面板\" refers to - it could be a Feishu bitable. \n\nLet me try searching through the account files to see what's actually there. Based on what I can see, the seven core accounts are legacy_base, defensive, balanced, aggressive, exit_dual, exit_tight, and alpha55, with breadth_aggressive being an additional one, which would give us eight total.","thinkingSignature":"6b8d74341cc2770a6dc32309ffb0846e2181e1821f632a7873851aa7b346a03e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ci7g35dux0ht_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport json, glob, os\nreports_dir = '/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports'\n\n# Find all account/live files to identify distinct paper trading accounts\npatterns = [\n    'paper_account_v1_latest.json',\n    'paper_aggressive_account_v1_latest.json',\n    'paper_balanced_account_v1_latest.json',\n    'paper_defensive_account_v1_latest.json',\n    'paper_alpha55_account_v1_latest.json',\n    'paper_v4_3_aggressive_account_v1_latest.json',\n    'paper_exit_dual_account_v1_latest.json',\n    'paper_exit_tight_account_v1_latest.json',\n    'breadth_aggressive_paper_latest.json',\n    'paper_shadow_*_latest.json',\n]\n\naccount_names = {\n    'paper_account_v1': '主链路 combo_v1',\n    'paper_aggressive_account_v1': 'Aggressive 18%'