{"type":"message","id":"a8b69589","parentId":"c8055f7d","timestamp":"2026-04-14T10:36:03.904Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have data for 7 paper trading accounts (excluding the main combo_v1 which uses a different file). But Zhang Ling says there are 9. Let me also check:\n1. The breadth aggressive paper\n2. Maybe there's a \"strict OOS\" paper\n\nLet me also check if the \"量化面板\" she's referring to is a Feishu bitable that I can access.\n\nActually, the document says 7 accounts as of March 26. But there might be 2 more now (breadth + strict OOS). So 9 total:\n1. legacy_base (combo_v1)\n2. defensive\n3. balanced\n4. aggressive\n5. exit_dual\n6. exit_tight\n\n\n7. alpha55\n8. breadth_aggressive\n9. strict OOS breadth\n\nThat would make 9! Let me check the strict OOS paper metrics.","thinkingSignature":"d4604910bb71cedacbfdc7aa2f3107911a20cee09f0349a7fb1ae60738726c39"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3s9u6oa00fxv_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport json, glob\nreports_dir = '/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports'\n\n# Breadth strict OOS\ncandidates = sorted(glob.glob(reports_dir + '/breadth_strict_oos_paper_2*.json'))\nif candidates:\n    d = json.load(open(candidates[-1]))\n    m = d.get('metrics', d)\n    ann = m.get('annual_return_pct', m.get('strategy_annual_return_pct', 'N/A'))\n    dd = m.get('max_drawdown_pct', m.get('strategy_max_drawdown_pct', 'N/A'))\n    sp = m.get('sharpe', m.get('strategy_sharpe', 'N/A'))\n    tot = m.get('total_return_pct', m.get('strategy_total_return_pct', 'N/A'))\n    print(f'Breadth Strict OOS [{candidates[-1].split(\\\"_\\\")[-1].replace(\\\".json\\\",\\\"\\\")}]: tot={tot}% ann={ann}% dd={dd}% sharpe={sp}')\n    print('Keys:', list(d.keys())[:10])\n\" 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":90763,"output":466,"cacheRead":35571,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126800,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776162947230,"responseId":"062d4b8b99b8ded0570c5a48d717e52f"}}
