{"type":"message","id":"aaecbcd3","parentId":"96717f58","timestamp":"2026-04-14T10:45:41.384Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_1bq5tie9de4u_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"23:PREDICTIONS_PATH = DATA_DIR / \"ml_predictions.csv\"\n24:LIVE_PREDICTIONS_PATH = DATA_DIR / \"ml_predictions_live_latest.csv\"\n25:FEATURES_PATH = DATA_DIR / \"ml_features_full.csv\"\n145:                    df = D.features([sym], [\"$close\"], start, end, freq=\"day\")\n162:def load_feature_latest_date() -> str | None:\n204:    feature_latest_date = load_feature_latest_date()\n210:    # Check 1: signal vs feature (relative staleness)\n211:    if feature_latest_date:\n212:        lag_days = (datetime.strptime(feature_latest_date, \"%Y-%m-%d\").date() - latest_date.date()).days\n216:            stale_reason = f\"信号已过期：预测文件最新日期 {signal_date}，但特征数据已到 {feature_latest_date}，落后 {lag_days} 天\"\n217:    # Check 2: signal vs today (absolute staleness — catches case where both feature and signal are old)\n229:        f\"需运行 Qlib 每日特征/预测更新流程，或手动刷新 ml_predictions.csv 到最新交易日后重试。\"\n235:        \"feature_latest_date\": feature_latest_date,\n427:        feat_date = signal_meta.get(\"feature_latest_date\", \"-\")\n536:        \"feature_latest_date\": signal_meta.get(\"feature_latest_date\"),\n632:    if signal_meta.get(\"feature_latest_date\"):\n633:        print(f\"特征最新日期: {signal_meta.get('feature_latest_date')}\")"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":9,"aggregated":"23:PREDICTIONS_PATH = DATA_DIR / \"ml_predictions.csv\"\n24:LIVE_PREDICTIONS_PATH = DATA_DIR / \"ml_predictions_live_latest.csv\"\n25:FEATURES_PATH = DATA_DIR / \"ml_features_full.csv\"\n145:                    df = D.features([sym], [\"$close\"], start, end, freq=\"day\")\n162:def load_feature_latest_date() -> str | None:\n204:    feature_latest_date = load_feature_latest_date()\n210:    # Check 1: signal vs feature (relative staleness)\n211:    if feature_latest_date:\n212:        lag_days = (datetime.strptime(feature_latest_date, \"%Y-%m-%d\").date() - latest_date.date()).days\n216:            stale_reason = f\"信号已过期：预测文件最新日期 {signal_date}，但特征数据已到 {feature_latest_date}，落后 {lag_days} 天\"\n217:    # Check 2: signal vs today (absolute staleness — catches case where both feature and signal are old)\n229:        f\"需运行 Qlib 每日特征/预测更新流程，或手动刷新 ml_predictions.csv 到最新交易日后重试。\"\n235:        \"feature_latest_date\": feature_latest_date,\n427:        feat_date = signal_meta.get(\"feature_latest_date\", \"-\")\n536:        \"feature_latest_date\": signal_meta.get(\"feature_latest_date\"),\n632:    if signal_meta.get(\"feature_latest_date\"):\n633:        print(f\"特征最新日期: {signal_meta.get('feature_latest_date')}\")","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776163541374}}
{"type":"message","id":"31106156","parentId":"aaecbcd3","timestamp":"2026-04-14T10:45:41.394Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_1bq5tie9de4u_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n宽度策略模拟盘\n- 默认参数仍兼容旧版进取盘\n- 支持通过命令行覆写参数，生成严格样本外版本的独立模拟盘\n\"\"\"\nimport sys, os\nsys.path.insert(0, os.path.dirname(__file__))\n\nimport multiprocessing as mp\nmp.freeze_support()\n\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\nimport json\nimport argparse\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nPROJECT_ROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[1]\nREPORT_DIR = PROJECT_ROOT / \"research\" / \"reports\"\nDATA_DIR = PROJECT_ROOT / \"data\" / \"ml_dataset_full\"\nPREDICTIONS_PATH = DATA_DIR / \"ml_predictions.csv\"\nLIVE_PREDICTIONS_PATH = DATA_DIR / \"ml_predictions_live_latest.csv\"\nFEATURES_PATH = DATA_DIR / \"ml_features_full.csv\"\nMAX_SIGNAL_LAG_DAYS = 2\nTODAY_STR = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\")\nTODAY_ISO = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\n\n\ndef append_history_records(summary: dict, slug: str) -> dict:\n    csv_path = REPORT_DIR / f\"{slug}_daily_history.csv\"\n    jsonl_path = REPORT_DIR / f\"{slug}_daily_history.jsonl\"\n    nav_history = summary.get(\"nav_history\", []) or []\n    compact_history: list[dict] = []\n    seen_markers: set[tuple[str, float, float]] = set()\n    for item in nav_history:\n        nav = round(float(item.get(\"nav\", 0.0)), 6)\n        cash = round(float(item.get(\"cash\", summary.get(\"cash\", 0.0))), 2)\n        marker = (str(item.get(\"date\") or summary.get(\"signal_date\")), nav, cash)\n        if marker in seen_markers:\n            continue\n        seen_markers.add(marker)\n        compact_history.append(item)\n    nav_history = compact_history\n    records: list[dict] = []\n    for idx, item in enumerate(nav_history):\n        nav = round(float(item.get(\"nav\", 0.0)), 6)\n        cash = round(float(item.get(\"cash\", summary.get(\"cash\", 0.0))), 2)\n        total_value = round(nav * float(summary.get(\"paper_capital\", 0.0)), 2)\n        market_value = round(total_value - cash, 2)\n        records.append(\n            {\n                \"generated_at\": f\"{summary.get('generated_at')}#{idx+1}\",\n                \"signal_date\": item.get(\"date\") or summary.get(\"signal_date\"),\n                \"nav\": nav,\n                \"total_value\": total_value,\n                \"cash\": cash,\n                \"market_value\": market_value,\n                \"position_count\": int(summary.get(\"position_count\", 0) or 0),"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":7,"aggregated":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n宽度策略模拟盘\n- 默认参数仍兼容旧版进取盘\n- 支持通过命令行覆写参数，生成严格样本外版本的独立模拟盘\n\"\"\"\nimport sys, os\nsys.path.insert(0, os.path.dirname(__file__))\n\nimport multiprocessing as mp\nmp.freeze_support()\n\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\nimport json\nimport argparse\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nPROJECT_ROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[1]\nREPORT_DIR = PROJECT_ROOT / \"research\" / \"reports\"\nDATA_DIR = PROJECT_ROOT / \"data\" / \"ml_dataset_full\"\nPREDICTIONS_PATH = DATA_DIR / \"ml_predictions.csv\"\nLIVE_PREDICTIONS_PATH = DATA_DIR / \"ml_predictions_live_latest.csv\"\nFEATURES_PATH = DATA_DIR / \"ml_features_full.csv\"\nMAX_SIGNAL_LAG_DAYS = 2\nTODAY_STR = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\")\nTODAY_ISO = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\n\n\ndef append_history_records(summary: dict, slug: str) -> dict:\n    csv_path = REPORT_DIR / f\"{slug}_daily_history.csv\"\n    jsonl_path = REPORT_DIR / f\"{slug}_daily_history.jsonl\"\n    nav_history = summary.get(\"nav_history\", []) or []\n    compact_history: list[dict] = []\n    seen_markers: set[tuple[str, float, float]] = set()\n    for item in nav_history:\n        nav = round(float(item.get(\"nav\", 0.0)), 6)\n        cash = round(float(item.get(\"cash\", summary.get(\"cash\", 0.0))), 2)\n        marker = (str(item.get(\"date\") or summary.get(\"signal_date\")), nav, cash)\n        if marker in seen_markers:\n            continue\n        seen_markers.add(marker)\n        compact_history.append(item)\n    nav_history = compact_history\n    records: list[dict] = []\n    for idx, item in enumerate(nav_history):\n        nav = round(float(item.get(\"nav\", 0.0)), 6)\n        cash = round(float(item.get(\"cash\", summary.get(\"cash\", 0.0))), 2)\n        total_value = round(nav * float(summary.get(\"paper_capital\", 0.0)), 2)\n        market_value = round(total_value - cash, 2)\n        records.append(\n            {\n                \"generated_at\": f\"{summary.get('generated_at')}#{idx+1}\",\n                \"signal_date\": item.get(\"date\") or summary.get(\"signal_date\"),\n                \"nav\": nav,\n                \"total_value\": total_value,\n                \"cash\": cash,\n                \"market_value\": market_value,\n                \"position_count\": int(summary.get(\"position_count\", 0) or 0),","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776163541384}}
{"type":"message","id":"71af799e","parentId":"31106156","timestamp":"2026-04-14T10:45:56.283Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the structure. The `run_breadth_paper_trading.py` reads from `ml_predictions_live_latest.csv` (predictions) and checks staleness. The key issue is that the predictions file was last modified on April 13 at 00:24 but only contains data up to April 3.\n\nLooking at the signal staleness logic:\n- `MAX_SIGNAL_LAG_DAYS = 2` - signals must be within 2 days\n- `signal_date` comes from the predictions file\n- The file was last modified at 00:24 on April 13, but predictions go only to April 3\n\nThe problem is: **清明节（4月4日-6日）休市三天，4月3日的预测之后就没有新预测了**。但奇怪的是4月7日开盘后为什么没有补上清明期间的预测？\n \nSo the predictions file has data through April 3, and there's no data for April 7 or later. But if the file was last modified on April 13 at 00:24, either someone manually ran a prediction script that failed to produce new data for the清明节假期, or the automated system never ran. Let me check if there's a cron job that should be updating the Qlib predictions, because looking at the dates, April 1, 2, and 3 have predictions but then there's a gap for the holiday period.\n\nThe script itself is just reading predictions from the file and shouldn't be responsible for generating them. The predictions are probably created by a separate Qlib training script, and I need to trace where that happens. Looking at the feature latest date and how the predictions are loaded, I should check the `load_feature_latest_date` function to understand how the prediction file gets updated in the first place.","thinkingSignature":"1d0c14c5df997e7aa908a1e44123c57855fd2c170fd8fea1ed4e48040f1de426"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3c9p7wydy50u_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '160,230p' /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_breadth_paper_trading.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":102117,"output":434,"cacheRead":35571,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":138122,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776163541395,"responseId":"062d4ddae7867d3f36dead17819f4a1e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e1de9384","parentId":"71af799e","timestamp":"2026-04-14T10:45:56.344Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_3c9p7wydy50u_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"def load_feature_latest_date() -> str | None:\n    if not FEATURES_PATH.exists():\n        return None\n    latest_date = None\n    try:\n        for chunk in pd.read_csv(FEATURES_PATH, usecols=[\"date\"], chunksize=500000):\n            dates = pd.to_datetime(chunk[\"date\"], errors=\"coerce\").dropna()\n            if len(dates) == 0:\n                continue\n            chunk_max = dates.max()\n            latest_date = chunk_max if latest_date is None or chunk_max > latest_date else latest_date\n    except Exception:\n        return None\n    return latest_date.date().isoformat() if latest_date is not None else None\n\n\ndef load_latest_signals(topk: int):\n    \"\"\"加载最新预测，优先 live 预测文件；若信号明显落后于特征最新日期，则标记为过期。\"\"\"\n    prediction_path = LIVE_PREDICTIONS_PATH if LIVE_PREDICTIONS_PATH.exists() else PREDICTIONS_PATH\n    preds = pd.read_csv(prediction_path, usecols=[\"date\", \"symbol\", \"pred_rank\"])\n    preds['date'] = pd.to_datetime(preds['date'], errors='coerce')\n    preds = preds.dropna(subset=['date', 'symbol', 'pred_rank']).copy()\n    latest_date = preds['date'].max()\n    latest = preds[preds['date'] == latest_date].copy()\n\n    # 过滤沪深300候选（主板+科创板）\n    hs300_mask = latest['symbol'].astype(str).str.match(r'^(000|001|002|003|600|601|603|688)')\n    hs300 = latest[hs300_mask].copy()\n\n    # 排除ST/*ST股票\n    try:\n        import tushare as ts\n        pro = ts.pro_api()\n        basic = pro.stock_basic(exchange='', list_status='L', fields='ts_code,name')\n        st_set = set(basic[basic['name'].str.contains('ST', na=False)]['ts_code'].tolist())\n        hs300 = hs300[~hs300['symbol'].isin(st_set)]\n        print(f\"  排除ST后候选数: {len(hs300)}\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"  ST过滤失败: {e}，跳过\")\n\n    top_stocks = hs300.sort_values('pred_rank', ascending=False).head(topk).copy()\n    signal_date = latest_date.date().isoformat()\n    feature_latest_date = load_feature_latest_date()\n    current_date = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\n    signal_lag_days = None\n    absolute_lag_days = None\n    stale_reason = \"\"\n    is_stale = False\n    # Check 1: signal vs feature (relative staleness)\n    if feature_latest_date:\n        lag_days = (datetime.strptime(feature_latest_date, \"%Y-%m-%d\").date() - latest_date.date()).days\n        signal_lag_days = max(lag_days, 0)\n        if lag_days > MAX_SIGNAL_LAG_DAYS:\n            is_stale = True\n            stale_reason = f\"信号已过期：预测文件最新日期 {signal_date}，但特征数据已到 {feature_latest_date}，落后 {lag_days} 天\"\n    # Check 2: signal vs today (absolute staleness — catches case where both feature and signal are old)\n    abs_lag = (datetime.strptime(current_date, \"%Y-%m-%d\").date() - latest_date.date()).days\n    absolute_lag_days = max(abs_lag, 0)\n    if absolute_lag_days > MAX_SIGNAL_LAG_DAYS:\n        is_stale = True\n        if stale_reason:\n            stale_reason += f\"；另：信号距今已实际过期 {absolute_lag_days} 天（当前日期 {current_date}）\"\n        else:\n            stale_reason = f\"信号已过期：预测文件最新日期 {signal_date}，距今已 {absolute_lag_days} 天未刷新（当前日期 {current_date}），超过阈值 {MAX_SIGNAL_LAG_DAYS} 天\"\n    refresh_hint = (\n        f\"提示：预测文件路径 {str(prediction_path)}；\"\n        f\"LIVE预测文件路径 {str(LIVE_PREDICTIONS_PATH)}（不存在）；\"\n        f\"需运行 Qlib 每日特征/预测更新流程，或手动刷新 ml_predictions.csv 到最新交易日后重试。\"\n    ) if is_stale else \"\""}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":5,"aggregated":"def load_feature_latest_date() -> str | None:\n    if not FEATURES_PATH.exists():\n        return None\n    latest_date = None\n    try:\n        for chunk in pd.read_csv(FEATURES_PATH, usecols=[\"date\"], chunksize=500000):\n            dates = pd.to_datetime(chunk[\"date\"], errors=\"coerce\").dropna()\n            if len(dates) == 0:\n                continue\n            chunk_max = dates.max()\n            latest_date = chunk_max if latest_date is None or chunk_max > latest_date else latest_date\n    except Exception:\n        return None\n    return latest_date.date().isoformat() if latest_date is not None else None\n\n\ndef load_latest_signals(topk: int):\n    \"\"\"加载最新预测，优先 live 预测文件；若信号明显落后于特征最新日期，则标记为过期。\"\"\"\n    prediction_path = LIVE_PREDICTIONS_PATH if LIVE_PREDICTIONS_PATH.exists() else PREDICTIONS_PATH\n    preds = pd.read_csv(prediction_path, usecols=[\"date\", \"symbol\", \"pred_rank\"])\n    preds['date'] = pd.to_datetime(preds['date'], errors='coerce')\n    preds = preds.dropna(subset=['date', 'symbol', 'pred_rank']).copy()\n    latest_date = preds['date'].max()\n    latest = preds[preds['date'] == latest_date].copy()\n\n    # 过滤沪深300候选（主板+科创板）\n    hs300_mask = latest['symbol'].astype(str).str.match(r'^(000|001|002|003|600|601|603|688)')\n    hs300 = latest[hs300_mask].copy()\n\n    # 排除ST/*ST股票\n    try:\n        import tushare as ts\n        pro = ts.pro_api()\n        basic = pro.stock_basic(exchange='', list_status='L', fields='ts_code,name')\n        st_set = set(basic[basic['name'].str.contains('ST', na=False)]['ts_code'].tolist())\n        hs300 = hs300[~hs300['symbol'].isin(st_set)]\n        print(f\"  排除ST后候选数: {len(hs300)}\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"  ST过滤失败: {e}，跳过\")\n\n    top_stocks = hs300.sort_values('pred_rank', ascending=False).head(topk).copy()\n    signal_date = latest_date.date().isoformat()\n    feature_latest_date = load_feature_latest_date()\n    current_date = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\n    signal_lag_days = None\n    absolute_lag_days = None\n    stale_reason = \"\"\n    is_stale = False\n    # Check 1: signal vs feature (relative staleness)\n    if feature_latest_date:\n        lag_days = (datetime.strptime(feature_latest_date, \"%Y-%m-%d\").date() - latest_date.date()).days\n        signal_lag_days = max(lag_days, 0)\n        if lag_days > MAX_SIGNAL_LAG_DAYS:\n            is_stale = True\n            stale_reason = f\"信号已过期：预测文件最新日期 {signal_date}，但特征数据已到 {feature_latest_date}，落后 {lag_days} 天\"\n    # Check 2: signal vs today (absolute staleness — catches case where both feature and signal are old)\n    abs_lag = (datetime.strptime(current_date, \"%Y-%m-%d\").date() - latest_date.date()).days\n    absolute_lag_days = max(abs_lag, 0)\n    if absolute_lag_days > MAX_SIGNAL_LAG_DAYS:\n        is_stale = True\n        if stale_reason:\n            stale_reason += f\"；另：信号距今已实际过期 {absolute_lag_days} 天（当前日期 {current_date}）\"\n        else:\n            stale_reason = f\"信号已过期：预测文件最新日期 {signal_date}，距今已 {absolute_lag_days} 天未刷新（当前日期 {current_date}），超过阈值 {MAX_SIGNAL_LAG_DAYS} 天\"\n    refresh_hint = (\n        f\"提示：预测文件路径 {str(prediction_path)}；\"\n        f\"LIVE预测文件路径 {str(LIVE_PREDICTIONS_PATH)}（不存在）；\"\n        f\"需运行 Qlib 每日特征/预测更新流程，或手动刷新 ml_predictions.csv 到最新交易日后重试。\"\n    ) if is_stale else \"\"","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776163556336}}
{"type":"message","id":"a99c0843","parentId":"e1de9384","timestamp":"2026-04-14T10:46:15.365Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see clearly: the `run_breadth_paper_trading.py` reads predictions from `LIVE_PREDICTIONS_PATH` (ml_predictions_live_latest.csv). This file exists and was last updated on April 13 at 00:24, but it only contains predictions through April 3.\n\nThe issue is:\n1. **清明节假期（4月4日-6日）A股休市**，所以4月3日之后没有交易日\n2. 4月7日（周二）开盘 - 应该生成4月3日的预测，但预测数据实际上**没有包含4月7日以后的新数据**\n\n\n3. The file modification timestamp of 00:24 on April 13 suggests it might have been generated after the holiday restarted, but there's no evidence of predictions for 4-07, 4-08, or 4-09. The \"LIVE预测文件路径\" message indicates this is supposed to be a separate live file, and the fact that it's still being referenced suggests predictions were never actually generated for the post-holiday trading days.\n\n4. There's likely a script that's supposed to run daily and generate new predictions, but it either hasn't been running or failed to execute—the file shows April 3 as the latest prediction date, so the prediction generation pipeline stopped working after that point.\n\n5. The real culprit might be that the Qlib prediction pipeline is broken and needs to be manually triggered to resume daily prediction generation.\n\nLet me look for the specific script responsible for creating `ml_predictions_live_latest.csv`.","thinkingSignature":"bf3371897bfaaf09db2d851c6bc88e991b14b080929c7846ab065929c1426954"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_od02zbqdv9uv_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 查找负责生成 ml_predictions_live_latest.csv 的脚本\ngrep -rn \"ml_predictions_live_latest\\|LIVE_PREDICTIONS\\|generate_extended\" \\\n  /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/ \\\n  --include=\"*.py\" 2>/dev/null | grep -v \".pyc\" | grep -v \"run_breadth\" | head -20"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_od02zbqdv9