{"type":"message","id":"1f9f8b82","parentId":"bea88229","timestamp":"2026-04-14T10:46:15.491Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_od02zbqdv9uv_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n增量预测生成：为 4/1-4/3 补充预测数据\n必须在所有 Qlib import 之前设置 fork 模式\n\"\"\"\nimport multiprocessing as mp\nmp.freeze_support()\nmp.set_start_method('fork', force=True)\n\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\nfrom pathlib import Path\nimport sys\nimport qlib\nfrom qlib.tests.config import get_gbdt_task\nfrom qlib.utils import init_instance_by_config\nfrom qlib.config import C\n\nC[\"joblib_backend\"] = \"sequential\"\nC[\"kernels\"] = 1\n\nROOT = Path(\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\")\nOUTPUT_CSV = ROOT / \"data/ml_predictions_live_latest.csv\"\n\n# ─── Step 1: 加载已有预测 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nprint(\"Loading existing predictions...\")\nexisting = pd.read_csv(OUTPUT_CSV, usecols=[\"date\", \"symbol\", \"pred_rank\"])\nexisting[\"date\"] = pd.to_datetime(existing[\"date\"]).dt.date\nprint(f\"  已有: {len(existing)} 行, 最新日期: {existing['date'].max()}\")\n\n# ─── Step 2: Qlib 初始化 ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nQLIB_LONG_ROOT = Path.home() / \".qlib/qlib_data/cn_data_long_2015_2026_180\"\nprint(\"Initializing Qlib...\")\nqlib.init(provider_uri=str(QLIB_LONG_ROOT), region=\"cn\")\n\n# ─── Step 3: 训练模型并预测 ──────────────────────────────────────────────────\nEXTEND_END = \"2026-04-11\"  # 上周五，最新可交易日\ntest_start = \"2023-01-03\"\n\nprint(f\"Training model with test_end={EXTEND_END} (may take 10-20min)...\")\ntask = get_gbdt_task(\n    handler_kwargs={\n        \"instruments\": \"universe180\",\n        \"start_time\": \"2015-01-05\",\n        \"end_time\": EXTEND_END,\n    },\n    dataset_kwargs={\n        \"train\": (\"2015-01-05\", \"2020-12-31\"),\n        \"valid\": (\"2021-01-01\", \"2022-12-30\"),\n        \"test\": (test_start, EXTEND_END),\n    },\n)\n\nmodel = init_instance_by_config(task[\"model\"])\ndataset = init_instance_by_config(task[\"dataset\"])\nprint(\"Fitting model...\")\nmodel.fit(dataset)\nprint(\"Predicting...\")\npred = model.predict(dataset, segment=\"test\")\nprint(f\"Predictions generated: {len(pred)} rows\")"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":6,"aggregated":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n增量预测生成：为 4/1-4/3 补充预测数据\n必须在所有 Qlib import 之前设置 fork 模式\n\"\"\"\nimport multiprocessing as mp\nmp.freeze_support()\nmp.set_start_method('fork', force=True)\n\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\nfrom pathlib import Path\nimport sys\nimport qlib\nfrom qlib.tests.config import get_gbdt_task\nfrom qlib.utils import init_instance_by_config\nfrom qlib.config import C\n\nC[\"joblib_backend\"] = \"sequential\"\nC[\"kernels\"] = 1\n\nROOT = Path(\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\")\nOUTPUT_CSV = ROOT / \"data/ml_predictions_live_latest.csv\"\n\n# ─── Step 1: 加载已有预测 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nprint(\"Loading existing predictions...\")\nexisting = pd.read_csv(OUTPUT_CSV, usecols=[\"date\", \"symbol\", \"pred_rank\"])\nexisting[\"date\"] = pd.to_datetime(existing[\"date\"]).dt.date\nprint(f\"  已有: {len(existing)} 行, 最新日期: {existing['date'].max()}\")\n\n# ─── Step 2: Qlib 初始化 ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nQLIB_LONG_ROOT = Path.home() / \".qlib/qlib_data/cn_data_long_2015_2026_180\"\nprint(\"Initializing Qlib...\")\nqlib.init(provider_uri=str(QLIB_LONG_ROOT), region=\"cn\")\n\n# ─── Step 3: 训练模型并预测 ──────────────────────────────────────────────────\nEXTEND_END = \"2026-04-11\"  # 上周五，最新可交易日\ntest_start = \"2023-01-03\"\n\nprint(f\"Training model with test_end={EXTEND_END} (may take 10-20min)...\")\ntask = get_gbdt_task(\n    handler_kwargs={\n        \"instruments\": \"universe180\",\n        \"start_time\": \"2015-01-05\",\n        \"end_time\": EXTEND_END,\n    },\n    dataset_kwargs={\n        \"train\": (\"2015-01-05\", \"2020-12-31\"),\n        \"valid\": (\"2021-01-01\", \"2022-12-30\"),\n        \"test\": (test_start, EXTEND_END),\n    },\n)\n\nmodel = init_instance_by_config(task[\"model\"])\ndataset = init_instance_by_config(task[\"dataset\"])\nprint(\"Fitting model...\")\nmodel.fit(dataset)\nprint(\"Predicting...\")\npred = model.predict(dataset, segment=\"test\")\nprint(f\"Predictions generated: {len(pred)} rows\")","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776163575485}}
{"type":"message","id":"67c036a7","parentId":"1f9f8b82","timestamp":"2026-04-14T10:46:32.115Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I found it! The `generate_extended_predictions.py` script generates the `ml_predictions_live_latest.csv` file. Looking at it:- It was created to \"补充预测数据\" for 4/1-4/3 (增量预测)\n- It extends predictions to `EXTEND_END = \"2026-04-11\"` (April 11, last Friday before the current period)- It uses Qlib with a GBDT model\n\nBut the issue is: **清明节是4月4日-6日**，所以4月3日之后就没有交易日了。4月7日开盘，4月11日是下一个周五。\n \nSo the predictions file last ran on April 13 at 00:24 and extended to April 11, but today's April 14 predictions aren't showing up—the script probably failed when it tried to run during the Qingming holiday when the market was closed.\n\nLooking at the daily cron schedule, there's no nightly job configured to generate new predictions each day. The `cron_breadth_paper_trading.sh` runs at 08:30 and loads existing predictions, but the script itself only reads from the file without regenerating it. The predictions file gets regenerated periodically through `generate_extended_predictions.py` and `train_ml_factors_all_a.py`, but these runs don't happen daily on a schedule—they're triggered manually or occasionally. So the pipeline is missing a daily cron at 16:30 or similar to refresh the Qlib predictions every evening after the market closes.\n\nThe current state shows the prediction file was last generated on April 13 at 00:24, which should have extended through April 11, but it's still only showing predictions through April 3—suggesting the script either failed to complete or the predictions weren't written to the file properly. I need to check if there's an issue with how `generate_extended_predictions.py` is writing to the file or if the cron job is actually running at all.","thinkingSignature":"5829ce535e524e0ed0bc0cd32666c36d90d2b9d6a2675d86339b0cbe6da00641"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_slpvold1ny9q_1