{"type":"message","id":"bf5546bc","parentId":"8f6b6a55","timestamp":"2026-04-14T10:47:55.240Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture:\n\n1. `tushare_to_qlib_update.py` - converts Tushare daily data to Qlib format\n2. There's NO cron for this script - it's run manually\n3. The Tushare data was updated on April 13 at 17:26, but the Qlib data was only updated on April 5 (清明节当天)\n4. So after the Qingming Festival, the Qlib data update pipeline was NOT run\n\nThe root cause: **清明节后，`tushare_to_qlib_update.py` 从未被执行**，导致 Qlib 数据停留在4月5日（清明节前一天），预测也只能跑到4月3日。\n\n\nSo the pipeline needs to flow through Tushare daily updates, then `tushare_to_qlib_update.py` to convert and append the data to Qlib, and finally `generate_extended_predictions.py` to create the model predictions. I need to verify that Tushare has the latest market data available before proceeding with the conversion step.","thinkingSignature":"f2ee7129e78393ae6b66807c1016500e43559a2a508a4a3078813f82ce311c84"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_p4deym6padjl_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/logs/download_tushare_update.log 2>/dev/null | tail -30"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_p4deym6padjl_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 确认今天（4月14日）Tushare数据是否是最新的\npython3 -c \"\nimport tushare as ts\nimport os\ntoken = os.getenv('TUSHARE_TOKEN', 'e3d8c68a414b9a84cbc49c637ec00875c7173a961eba98cff09c1afc')\npro = ts.pro_api(token)\ndf = pro.trade_cal(start_date='20260401', end_date='20260415')\nprint(df[df['is_open']==1])\n\" 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":108819,"output":408,"cacheRead":35571,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":144798,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776163663260,"responseId":"062d4e54b3e5df60864e91a4f32d41c0"}}
