{"type":"message","id":"99148cdd","parentId":"33f984cb","timestamp":"2026-04-14T10:48:59.696Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The trade_date column has some issue - the dates are getting parsed as timestamps. But the point is: the last 5 entries have dates \"2026-04-03\", \"2026-04-07\", \"2026-04-08\", \"2026-04-09\", \"2026-04-10\" (stored as weird epoch values because of parsing). These are the correct last 5 trading days.\n\nFrom the Tushare log, the last update was on April 13 at 16:03 and it updated to 2026-04-10 (清明后第一个完整交易周). So:\n- Tushare data: updated to April 10 ✅\n\n\n- Qlib data: stops at April 3 ❌ (清明节前一天)\n- Predictions: only to April 3 ❌\n\nThe root cause is becoming clearer: after Qingming Festival, `tushare_to_qlib_update.py` never ran to convert the new Tushare data into Qlib format, so the predictions pipeline never received fresh data to work with.\n\nThe fix is to run `tushare_to_qlib_update.py` starting from April 3 through today (April 14), then execute `generate_extended_predictions.py` to extend predictions through April 14. I should also set up a daily cron job to keep this pipeline running automatically going forward.","thinkingSignature":"3b34edfe9cfaffe72795003c66f5f4d1bab657abdafd978cc05d4665758d25a3"},{"type":"text","text":"根因找到了。给你说清楚：\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 根因：清明节后 Qlib 数据管道断掉\n\n**数据流：**\n```\nTushare 日频数据\n    ↓ download_tushare_update.log（4月13日16:03更新到 04/10）\n    ↓ 【清明后没执行】tushare_to_qlib_update.py\n    ↓ Qlib 特征数据（停在 04/03）\n    ↓ 【清明后没执行】generate_extended_predictions.py\n    ↓ ml_predictions_live_latest.csv（停在 04/03）\n```\n\n清明节（4/4-4/6）后：\n- ✅ 4/13 Tushare 更新到了 4/10 数据\n- ❌ 但 `tushare_to_qlib_update.py` 从未执行 → Qlib 数据停在 4/3\n- ❌ 预测也只能跑到 4/3\n\n---\n\n需要我现在执行**两步修复**：\n\n1. **立即补数据**：运行 `tushare_to_qlib_update.py` 把清明后的数据（4/3→4/10）补进 Qlib，然后跑 `generate_extended_predictions.py` 生成清明后的预测\n2. **加每日 cron**：在每天 16:30 自动跑 `tushare_to_qlib_update.py` + `generate_extended_predictions.py`，避免再次断掉\n\n要我现在开始吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":112200,"output":586,"cacheRead":35571,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":148357,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776163721145,"responseId":"062d4e8e729b584bc5fcc17eead31947"}}
