{"type":"message","id":"58fbd8e8","parentId":"418532cf","timestamp":"2026-04-14T11:21:23.132Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The task config looks correct. The issue is that it's using the `Alpha158` handler which loads 158 features for all instruments in `universe180`, and the training segment is 2015-2020 (5 years) with validation 2021-2022 and test 2023-2026.\n\nThe problem is that this is a HUGE dataset. With `num_threads=20`, LightGBM will try to use lots of memory for parallel training.\n\nThe fix could be:\n1. Reduce the number of threads\n2. Reduce the training data range\n3. Use a smaller subset of instruments\n\nBut more importantly - the previous successful runs of this script were working. So something changed. \n\nWait, the script was killed during the `model.fit(dataset)` call with SIGKILL, which points to the OOM killer rather than a code issue. Looking at the memory stats, there's about 8.5GB free, but the training is probably trying to allocate more than that. I could reduce the thread count with `OMP_NUM_THREADS=1`, limit LightGBM's threads directly, or trim the training period. Let me write a modified version of the script that handles this more carefully.\n\nActually, I'm realizing the real issue might be the dataset size itself—it's loading the entire 11-year history with 158 features for 180 instruments, which is massive. Let me try running with just 2 threads and see if that helps.","thinkingSignature":"17b69bc16525ec0dc1b0dbba5178d7fef7c4f028f24f18f9287e3cf00aad5a8c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_m33kj88u21it_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/run_extended_predictions.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"精简版预测生成 - 限制内存使用\"\"\"\nimport multiprocessing as mp\nmp.freeze_support()\nimport os\nos.environ[\"OMP_NUM_THREADS\"] = \"2\"\nos.environ[\"MKL_NUM_THREADS\"] = \"2\"\nos.environ[\"OPENBLAS_NUM_THREADS\"] = \"2\"\n\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\nfrom pathlib import Path\nimport sys\n\nROOT = Path(\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\")\nOUTPUT_CSV = ROOT / \"data/ml_dataset_full/ml_predictions_live_latest.csv\"\n\nprint(\"Loading existing predictions...\")\nexisting = pd.read_csv(OUTPUT_CSV, usecols=[\"date\", \"symbol\", \"pred_rank\"])\nexisting[\"date\"] = pd.to_datetime(existing[\"date\"]).dt.date\nprint(f\"  已有: {len(existing)} 行, 最新日期: {existing['date'].max()}\")\n\nprint(\"Initializing Qlib...\")\nimport qlib\nfrom qlib.tests.config import get_gbdt_task\nfrom qlib.utils import init_instance_by_config\n\nqlib.init(provider_uri=str(Path.home() / \".qlib/qlib_data/cn_data_long_2015_2026_180\"), region=\"cn\")\n\nEXTEND_END = \"2026-04-11\"\ntask = get_gbdt_task(\n    handler_kwargs={\"instruments\": \"universe180\", \"start_time\": \"2015-01-05\", \"end_time\": EXTEND_END},\n    dataset_kwargs={\n        \"train\": (\"2015-01-05\", \"2020-12-31\"),\n        \"valid\": (\"2021-01-01\", \"2022-12-30\"),\n        \"test\": (\"2023-01-03\", EXTEND_END),\n    },\n)\n# Reduce threads for memory\ntask[\"model\"][\"kwargs\"][\"num_threads\"] = 2\nprint(f\"Training model (threads=2, test_end={EXTEND_END})...\")\n\nmodel = init_instance_by_config(task[\"model\"])\ndataset = init_instance_by_config(task[\"dataset\"])\nmodel.fit(dataset)\nprint(\"Predicting...\")\npred = model.predict(dataset, segment=\"test\")\nprint(f\"Predictions: {len(pred)} rows\")\n\npred_df = pred.reset_index()\npred_df.columns = [\"date\", \"symbol\", \"pred\"]\npred_df[\"date\"] = pd.to_datetime(pred_df[\"date\"]).dt.date\npred_df[\"pred_rank\"] = pred_df.groupby(\"date\")[\"pred\"].rank(pct=True)\n\ncutoff = pd.Timestamp(\"2026-04-01\").date()\nnew_only = pred_df[pred_df[\"date\"] >= cutoff].copy()\nprint(f\"New dates (>= 2026-04-01): {len(new_only)} 行, {new_only['date'].min()} → {new_only['date'].max()}\")\n\nif len(new_only) == 0:\n    print(\"No new dates - model may not have extended beyond 2026-03-31.\")\n    sys.exit(0)\n\ncombined = pd.concat([existing, new_only], ignore_index=True)\ncombined = combined.drop_duplicates(subset=[\"date\", \"symbol\"], keep=\"last\")\ncombined = combined.sort_values([\"date\", \"pred_rank\"], ascending=[True, False])\ncombined[\"date\"] = pd.to_datetime(combined[\"date\"]).dt.strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\ncombined.to_csv(OUTPUT_CSV, index=False)\n\nprint(f\"\\nSaved: {OUTPUT_CSV}\")\nprint(f\"Total: {len(combined)} 行, {combined['date'].min()} → {combined['date'].max()}\")\nprint(f\"New dates: {sorted(new_only['date'].unique())}\")\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":119511,"output":1115,"cacheRead":35571,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":156197,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776165656335,"responseId":"062d561d4a54f2bb779da1acea54b74c"}}
