{"type":"message","id":"1ea7d0b3","parentId":"4d40fcb4","timestamp":"2026-04-14T11:22:12.832Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, I should not write to `/tmp/` and execute from there. The issue is that the exec preflight is blocking because of \"complex interpreter invocation\". The `/tmp/run_extended_predictions.py` has `import qlib` and `from qlib.tests.config import get_gbdt_task` which are complex imports. Let me think of a different approach.\n\nActually, the exec preflight is specifically blocking `python3 -c \"...\"` or `python3 <script>` invocations with complex imports. But it allows `python3 /path/to/script.py` as long as the script doesn't trigger the preflight check. \n\nThe preflight check is blocking any Python invocation that uses complex imports like `import pandas`, `import numpy`, or `import qlib` — even simple pandas operations get flagged as complex. The script I'm trying to run does have these imports, so it'll likely be blocked too. Maybe instead I should focus on why the script is getting killed with SIGKILL rather than trying to work around the preflight check.\n\nLooking at the sequence: Qlib initializes, data loads successfully in about 107 seconds, then right when `model.fit(dataset)` starts, the process gets killed instantly. That's the critical point — the model fitting is what's triggering the OOM killer.\n\nThe issue is likely memory spikes during dataset initialization or gradient computation. Rather than fighting the memory limits, I could try reducing the dataset size or switching to incremental training with LightGBM's `init` method instead of full retraining. But honestly, the simplest fix is probably to wait until tomorrow after the market closes when there's more free memory available, then try running the script again.\n\nOr I could try writing a minimal script that uses LightGBM's native API directly instead of going through Qlib's abstraction layer, which would give me more control over the training process.","thinkingSignature":"614c27746df2d3407a587ed76444547e48c306cdf0bcaafce541c635ee565561"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_u9k398lieurn_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/generate_extended_predictions_lite.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"精简版预测生成 - 使用轻量LightGBM直接加载Qlib数据，避免OOM\"\"\"\nimport multiprocessing as mp\nmp.freeze_support()\nimport os\n# 限制线程数避免内存爆炸\nos.environ[\"OMP_NUM_THREADS\"] = \"2\"\nos.environ[\"MKL_NUM_THREADS\"] = \"2\"\nos.environ[\"OPENBLAS_NUM_THREADS\"] = \"2\"\n\nimport sys\nfrom pathlib import Path\nROOT = Path(\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\")\nsys.path.insert(0, str(ROOT))\nsys.path.insert(0, str(ROOT / \"scripts\"))\n\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\nimport lightgbm as lgb\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\nOUTPUT_CSV = ROOT / \"data/ml_dataset_full/ml_predictions_live_latest.csv\"\nQLIB_URI = str(Path.home() / \".qlib/qlib_data/cn_data_long_2015_2026_180\")\n\nprint(\"=== [1/6] 加载已有预测 ===\")\nexisting = pd.read_csv(OUTPUT_CSV, usecols=[\"date\", \"symbol\", \"pred_rank\"])\nexisting[\"date\"] = pd.to_datetime(existing[\"date\"]).dt.date\nprint(f\"  已有: {len(existing)} 行, 最新日期: {existing['date'].max()}\")\n\nprint(\"=== [2/6] 初始化Qlib ===\")\nimport qlib\nqlib.init(provider_uri=QLIB_URI, region=\"cn\")\nfrom qlib.data import D\n\nprint(\"=== [3/6] 加载特征（Alpha158简化版） ===\")\n# 使用简化特征集，仅核心量价特征\nBASE_FEATURES = [\"$close\", \"$open\", \"$high\", \"$low\", \"$volume\", \"$amount\",\n                 \"$roc5\", \"$roc10\", \"$roc20\",\n                 \"$rsi5\", \"$rsi10\", \"$rsi20\",\n                 \"$volume_ratio\", \"$amount_ratio\"]\n\nINSTRUMENTS = \"universe180\"\nEND_DATE = \"2026-04-11\"\n\nprint(f\"  加载个股列表: {INSTRUMENTS}\")\ninstruments = D.instruments(INSTRUMENTS)\nprint(f\"  个股数: {len(instruments)}\")\n\nprint(\"  生成日期列表...\")\nall_dates = D.trade_days(start_time=\"2023-01-03\", end_time=END_DATE)\nprint(f\"  交易日数量: {len(all_dates)}\")\n\n# 分批处理避免OOM\nprint(\"  分批加载数据...\")\nBATCH_SIZE = 30\ndates = [str(d)[:10] for d in all_dates]\nrecords = []\n\nfor i in range(0, len(dates), BATCH_SIZE):\n    batch_dates = dates[i:i+BATCH_SIZE]\n    batch_str = \",\".join(batch_dates)\n    try:\n        fields = [\"$symbol\"] + [f.replace(\"$\",\"\") for f in BASE_FEATURES]\n        df = D.features(instruments, fields, start_time=batch_dates[0], end_time=batch_dates[-1], freq=\"day\")\n        df = df.reset_index()\n        df.columns = [\"date\", \"symbol\"] + fields[1:]\n        records.append(df)\n        if (i // BATCH_SIZE) % 5 == 0:\n            print(f\"  加载进度: {i+BATCH_SIZE}/{len(dates)} ({len(records)} batches)\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"  批次 {i} 失败: {e}\")\n        continue\n\ndata = pd.concat(records, ignore_index=True)\nprint(f\"  总记录: {len(data)} 行\")\n\n# 清理\nfor r in records:\n    del r\ndel records\n\nprint(\"=== [4/6] 特征工程 ===\")\ndata[\"date\"] = pd.to_datetime(data[\"date\"]).dt.date\nfor col in [\"close\",\"open\",\"high\",\"low\"]:\n    if col in data.columns:\n        data[col] = pd.to_numeric(data[col], errors=\"coerce\")\nif \"volume\" in data.columns:\n    data[\"volume\"] = pd.to_numeric(data[\"volume\"], errors=\"coerce\").fillna(0)\n\n# 计算简单特征\ndata[\"returns\"] = data.groupby(\"symbol\")[\"close\"].pct_change(5)\ndata[\"volatility\"] = data.groupby(\"symbol\")[\"close\"].pct_change().rolling(10).std()\ndata[\"volume_ma5\"] = data.groupby(\"symbol\")[\"volume\"].transform(lambda x: x.rolling(5).mean())\ndata[\"volume_ratio\"] = data[\"volume\"] / data[\"volume_ma5\"].replace(0, 1)\n\nfeature_cols = [\"close\",\"open\",\"high\",\"low\",\"volume\",\"returns\",\"volatility\",\"volume_ratio\"]\nfor c in feature_cols:\n    if c not in data.columns:\n        data[c] = 0\ndata = data.dropna(subset=[\"date\",\"symbol\",\"close\"])\ndata = data[data[\"close\"] > 0]\n\nprint(f\"  有效记录: {len(data)} 行\")\n\nprint(\"=== [5/6] 训练LightGBM ===\")\ntrain_data = data[data[\"date\"] <= pd.Timestamp(\"2020-12-31\").date()].copy()\ntest_data = data[data[\"date\"] >= pd.Timestamp(\"2023-01-03\").date()].copy()\n\nX_train = train_data[feature_cols].fillna(0).values\ny_train = train_data[\"close\"].pct_change(5).fillna(0).values\nX_test = test_data[feature_cols].fillna(0).values\n\nprint(f\"  训练集: {X_train.shape}, 测试集: {X_test.shape}\")\n\nlgb_train = lgb.Dataset(X_train, y_train, feature_name=feature_cols, free_raw_data=True)\nlgb_test = lgb.Dataset(X_test, feature_name=feature_cols, reference=lgb_train, free_raw_data=True)\n\nparams = {\n    \"objective\": \"mse\",\n    \"num_leaves\": 31,\n    \"learning_rate\": 0.05,\n    \"num_threads\": 2,\n    \"verbose\": -1,\n}\n\nprint(\"  开始训练...\")\nmodel = lgb.train(\n    params,\n    lgb_train,\n    num_boost_round=100,\n    valid_sets=[lgb_test],\n    callbacks=[lgb.log_evaluation(50)],\n)\nprint(\"  训练完成\")\n\n# 预测\ntest_data[\"pred\"] = model.predict(X_test)\ntest_data[\"pred_rank\"] = test_data.groupby(\"date\")[\"pred\"].rank(pct=True)\ntest_data[\"date\"] = pd.to_datetime(test_data[\"date\"]).dt.date\n\n# 合并\nprint(\"=== [6/6] 合并写入 ===\")\ncutoff = pd.Timestamp(\"2026-04-01\").date()\nnew_only = test_data[test_data[\"date\"] >= cutoff][[\"date\",\"symbol\",\"pred_rank\"]].copy()\nprint(f\"  新增日期 (>= 4/01): {len(new_only)} 行\")\nprint(f\"  新增日期范围: {new_only['date'].min()} ~ {new_only['date'].max()}\")\n\nif len(new_only) == 0:\n    print(\"  无新增，跳过写入\")\n    sys.exit(0)\n\ncombined = pd.concat([existing, new_only], ignore_index=True)\ncombined = combined.drop_duplicates(subset=[\"date\", \"symbol\"], keep=\"last\")\ncombined = combined.sort_values([\"date\", \"pred_rank\"], ascending=[True, False])\ncombined[\"date\"] = pd.to_datetime(combined[\"date\"]).dt.strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\ncombined.to_csv(OUTPUT_CSV, index=False)\n\nprint(f\"  ✅ 已保存: {OUTPUT_CSV}\")\nprint(f\"  总记录: {len(combined)} 行\")\nprint(f\"  日期范围: {combined['date'].min()} ~ {combined['date'].max()}\")\nprint(f\"  新增日期: {sorted(new_only['date'].unique())}\")\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":120656,"output":2133,"cacheRead":35571,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":158360,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776165683170,"responseId":"062d5637de5aca6040070aacf84866c4"}}
