{"type":"message","id":"97a0fd36","parentId":"a2b1cfe9","timestamp":"2026-04-14T11:26:17.461Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-14 19:10:08 GMT+8] Feishu[coding-agent] DM | 张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae) [msg:om_x100b52d6462414acb3b2194184a1a69]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52d6462414acb3b2194184a1a69\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-14 19:10 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\n开始"}],"timestamp":1776165977454}}
{"type":"message","id":"a7b2df92","parentId":"97a0fd36","timestamp":"2026-04-14T11:27:18.664Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user sent \"开始\" again. Let me continue fixing the prediction pipeline. The main issue is that `generate_extended_predictions.py` uses Qlib's dataset which loads all data into memory and gets killed by OOM.\n\nLet me take a different approach - use the existing `train_ml_factors_all_a.py` approach which uses the locally stored data from `tushare_a_all/` directory instead of loading from Qlib dynamically. But the issue is that `a_stock_daily_merged.csv` only goes to 2021.\n\nActually, let me check what the cleanest approach is. Looking at the Qlib data situation:\n\n\n- The Qlib features directory has 77,947 subdirectories (one per stock), but the `all.txt` file was just updated on April 13\n- The issue is that Qlib's Python API for instruments is broken - it returns a dict instead of a list, though the underlying data files are fine\n\nI think the best path forward is to load predictions directly from the Qlib feature CSVs using a simple script that reads from the `~/.qlib/qlib_data/cn_data_long_2015_2026_180/features/` directory instead of going through Qlib's dataset interface.\n\nThe feature format is `{stock_code}/{field}.csv` where each CSV has a date-indexed structure with the stock code as the column name. Since I can't load all 77,947 stocks at once, I'll need to either use the `all.txt` file to identify which stocks were active on each target date and sample a subset, or limit myself to just the most liquid stocks. But the script is getting SIGKILLed during training when Qlib loads all 77,947 stocks at once with 180 features over 11 years—that's roughly 124 million rows and 50+ GB of memory. The model only has 2GB to work with, so I need to either restrict the stock universe to something like the top 500 by market cap or use the smaller `universe180` dataset, and also trim the feature set and time period to fit within memory constraints. The SIGKILL is happening during data loading, not model training, so I need to load a subset of stocks instead of all 77,947. I'm going to read the universe180.txt file directly to get the stock list, then batch the feature loading by date ranges rather than trying to load everything at once, and keep only essential features to minimize memory usage.","thinkingSignature":"10c8e1acc03fd4fb1b11eb33d57f609929dd973e40fc7cb483a50cc851888f51"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_sebn8uc1x0og_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/generate_predictions_from_qlib_dir.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"从Qlib目录直接读取特征文件，生成预测（避免Qlib DatasetH全量加载OOM）\"\"\"\nimport os\nos.environ[\"OMP_NUM_THREADS\"] = \"4\"\nos.environ[\"MKL_NUM_THREADS\"] = \"4\"\nos.environ[\"OPENBLAS_NUM_THREADS\"] = \"4\"\n\nimport sys\nfrom pathlib import Path\nROOT = Path(\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\")\nsys.path.insert(0, str(ROOT))\n\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\nimport lightgbm as lgb\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\n\nQLIB_DIR = Path.home() / \".qlib/qlib_data/cn_data_long_2015_2026_180\"\nOUTPUT_CSV = ROOT / \"data/ml_dataset_full/ml_predictions_live_latest.csv\"\n\n# ============================================================\nprint(\"=== [1/5] 读取universe180列表 ===\")\nuniverse_file = QLIB_DIR / \"instruments/universe180.txt\"\nstock_dates = {}\nwith open(universe_file) as f:\n    for line in f:\n        parts = line.strip().split()\n        if len(parts) >= 3:\n            stock, start, end = parts[0], parts[1], parts[2]\n            stock_dates[stock] = (start, end)\n\n# Filter to stocks active on target dates\nTARGET_START = \"2026-04-01\"\nTARGET_END = \"2026-04-11\"\nactive_stocks = [\n    s for s, (start, end) in stock_dates.items()\n    if start <= TARGET_END and end >= TARGET_START\n]\nprint(f\"  活跃股票数: {len(active_stocks)}\")\n\n# ============================================================\nprint(\"=== [2/5] 加载日历 ===\")\ncal_file = QLIB_DIR / \"calendars/all.txt\"\ntrade_dates = []\nwith open(cal_file) as f:\n    for line in f:\n        line = line.strip()\n        if line >= \"2023-01-01\" and line <= TARGET_END:\n            trade_dates.append(line)\ntrade_dates.sort()\nprint(f\"  交易日数(2023+): {len(trade_dates)}\")\n\n# ============================================================\nprint(\"=== [3/5] 分批加载特征 ===\")\nFEATURES_DIR = QLIB_DIR / \"features\"\n# 核心特征列表（精简）\nFIELDS = [\"close\", \"open\", \"high\", \"low\", \"volume\", \"amount\",\n          \"vwap5\", \"roc5\", \"roc10\", \"roc20\",\n          \"rsi5\", \"rsi10\", \"rsi20\",\n          \"volume5\", \"volume20\", \"volume_ratio\"]\n\n# 按时间分批，每次加载1个月的数据\nfrom datetime import datetime\nstart_dt = datetime(2023, 1, 1)\nend_dt = datetime(2026, 4, 11)\nbatch_days = 60  # 每批60天\ncurrent_dt = start_dt\nbatch_dfs = []\nbatch_num = 0\n\nwhile current_dt <= end_dt:\n    batch_end = min(current_dt + timedelta(days=batch_days), end_dt)\n    batch_str_start = current_dt.strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\n    batch_str_end = batch_end.strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\n    batch_num += 1\n\n    # 收集本批次所有股票的数据\n    records = []\n    for stock in active_stocks:\n        stock_dir = FEATURES_DIR / stock\n        if not stock_dir.exists():\n            continue\n        for field in FIELDS:\n            fpath = stock_dir / f\"{field}.csv\"\n            if not fpath.exists():\n                continue\n            try:\n                col_df = pd.read_csv(fpath, index_col=0, names=[\"date\", field])\n                col_df.index = pd.to_datetime(col_df.index).strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\n                col_df = col_df[(col_df.index >= batch_str_start) & (col_df.index <= batch_str_end)]\n                if not col_df.empty:\n                    col_df[\"symbol\"] = stock\n                    col_df[\"date_idx\"] = col_df.index\n                    records.append(col_df[[\"date_idx\", \"symbol\", field]])\n            except:\n                continue\n        if batch_num % 20 == 0 and stock == active_stocks[0]:\n            print(f\"  Batch {batch_num}: {batch_str_start}~{batch_str_end}\")\n\n    if records:\n        batch_df = records[0].set_index([\"date_idx\",\"symbol\"]).join(\n            [r.set_index([\"date_idx\",\"symbol\"]) for r in records[1:]], how=\"outer\"\n        ).reset_index()\n        batch_dfs.append(batch_df)\n        print(f\"  Batch {batch_num}: {batch_str_start}~{batch_str_end} -> {len(batch_df)} rows\")\n\n    current_dt = batch_end + timedelta(days=1)\n\nprint(f\"  总计 {len(batch_dfs)} 批次\")\nif batch_dfs:\n    data = pd.concat(batch_dfs, ignore_index=True)\n    print(f\"  总记录: {len(data)} 行\")\nelse:\n    print(\"  ERROR: No data loaded!\")\n    sys.exit(1)\n\n# ============================================================\nprint(\"=== [4/5] 特征工程 ===\")\ndata[\"date\"] = pd.to_datetime(data[\"date_idx\"]).dt.date\nfor col in FIELDS:\n    if col in data.columns:\n        data[col] = pd.to_numeric(data[col], errors=\"coerce\")\ndata = data.dropna(subset=[\"date\",\"symbol\",\"close\"])\ndata = data[data[\"close\"] > 0]\n\n# 计算特征\nfor n in [5, 10, 20]:\n    data[f\"close_roc{n}\"] = data.groupby(\"symbol\")[\"close\"].pct_change(n)\n    if f\"volume{n}\" in data.columns:\n        data[f\"vol_ma{n}\"] = data.groupby(\"symbol\")[f\"volume{n}\"].transform(lambda x: x.rolling(n, min_periods=1).mean())\n    else:\n        data[f\"vol_ma{n}\"] = data.groupby(\"symbol\")[\"volume\"].transform(lambda x: x.rolling(n, min_periods=1).mean())\n\ndata[\"vol_ratio\"] = data[\"volume\"] / data[\"vol_ma5\"].replace(0, 1)\nfor n in [5, 10, 20]:\n    if f\"close_roc{n}\" in data.columns:\n        data[f\"rsi{n}\"] = data.groupby(\"symbol\")[f\"close_roc{n}\"].transform(\n            lambda x: (x > 0).rolling(n, min_periods=1).mean() * 100\n        )\n\nfeature_cols = [\"close\", \"open\", \"high\", \"low\", \"volume\",\n                \"close_roc5\", \"close_roc10\", \"close_roc20\",\n                \"vol_ratio\", \"rsi5\", \"rsi10\", \"rsi20\"]\nfor c in feature_cols:\n    if c not in data.columns:\n        data[c] = 0\n\ndata = data.dropna(subset=[\"date\"] + feature_cols)\nprint(f\"  有效记录: {len(data)} 行, 日期范围: {data['date'].min()} ~ {data['date'].max()}\")\n\n# ============================================================\nprint(\"=== [5/5] 训练+预测 ===\")\ntrain = data[data[\"date\"] <= pd.Timestamp(\"2020-12-31\").date()].copy()\ntest = data[data[\"date\"] >= pd.Timestamp(\"2023-01-03\").date()].copy()\nprint(f\"  训练集: {len(train)}, 测试集: {len(test)}\")\n\nX_train = train[feature_cols].fillna(0).values\ny_train = train.groupby(\"symbol\")[\"close\"].pct_change(5).fillna(0).values\nX_test = test[feature_cols].fillna(0).values\n\nlgb_train = lgb.Dataset(X_train, y_train, feature_name=feature_cols, free_raw_data=True)\nlgb_test = lgb.Dataset(X_test, feature_name=feature_cols, reference=lgb_train, free_raw_data=True)\n\nparams = {\n    \"objective\": \"mse\",\n    \"num_leaves\": 31,\n    \"learning_rate\": 0.05,\n    \"num_threads\": 4,\n    \"verbose\": -1,\n    \"min_data_in_leaf\": 100,\n}\n\nmodel = lgb.train(params, lgb_train, num_boost_round=100,\n                  valid_sets=[lgb_test], callbacks=[lgb.log_evaluation(50)])\n\ntest[\"pred\"] = model.predict(X_test)\ntest[\"pred_rank\"] = test.groupby(\"date\")[\"pred\"].rank(pct=True)\n\n# ============================================================\nprint(\"=== [6/6] 合并写入 ===\")\nexisting = pd.read_csv(OUTPUT_CSV, usecols=[\"date\",\"symbol\",\"pred_rank\"])\nexisting[\"date\"] = pd.to_datetime(existing[\"date\"]).dt.date\nprint(f\"  已有: {len(existing)} 行, 最新: {existing['date'].max()}\")\n\ncutoff = pd.Timestamp(\"2026-04-01\").date()\nnew_only = test[test[\"date\"] >= cutoff][[\"date\",\"symbol\",\"pred_rank\"]].copy()\nnew_only[\"date\"] = pd.to_datetime(new_only[\"date\"]).dt.strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\nprint(f\"  新增: {len(new_only)} 行, 日期: {new_only['date'].min()} ~ {new_only['date'].max()}\")\nprint(f\"  新增的唯一日期: {sorted(new_only['date'].unique())}\")\n\nif len(new_only) == 0:\n    print(\"  无新增，跳过\")\n    sys.exit(0)\n\ncombined = pd.concat([existing, new_only], ignore_index=True)\ncombined = combined.drop_duplicates(subset=[\"date\",\"symbol\"], keep=\"last\")\ncombined = combined.sort_values([\"date\",\"pred_rank\"], ascending=[True,False])\ncombined[\"date\"] = pd.to_datetime(combined[\"date\"]).dt.strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\ncombined.to_csv(OUTPUT_CSV, index=False)\nprint(f\"  ✅ 已保存: {OUTPUT_CSV}\")\nprint(f\"  总: {len(combined)} 行, {combined['date'].min()} ~ {combined['date'].max()}\")\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":133,"output":2781,"cacheRead":35571,"cacheWrite":25121,"totalTokens":63606,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776165977461,"responseId":"062d575ba2870e9f4b98d47362a14117"}}
