{"type":"message","id":"41878b71","parentId":"3b3814ee","timestamp":"2026-04-14T11:30:33.051Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The Qlib data loading works. I can see:\n- 2026-04-01, 04-02, 04-03 (3 days) are loaded for these stocks\n- But we only have data up to 2026-04-10 in Qlib (4/11 would be predicted, not in Qlib yet)\n- Actually wait - we need 2026-04-11 to generate predictions for that date (T+1 prediction)\n\nBut we need to check: the calendar shows 2026-04-11 but I don't think there's 2026-04-11 data in the features. Let me check.Actually, from the earlier calendar check: `['2026-04-01', '2026-04-02', '2026-04-03', '2026-04-07', '2026-04-08', '2026-04-09', '2026-04-10']` - so 04-11 is a Saturday and not a trading day. \n\nSo the last trading day is 04-10, which means T+1 predictions can only go through 04-11 (Saturday), and 04-14 (Monday) would require data we don't have yet. For practical purposes, generating predictions for 04-07 through 04-10 would update the paper trading system, though ideally we'd need 04-11 data as well.\n\nThe core issue is that Tushare downloads stopped at 04-10, and since 04-11 and 04-12 are weekend days, the next trading opportunity would be 04-13 or 04-14. To properly predict 04-14 returns, I'd need features through at least 04-11 or 04-13, but that data doesn't exist yet. The predictions are also stale—04-07 predictions are already a week old.\n\nI'm realizing the pipeline has a fundamental limitation: Tushare refreshes at 16:00, but we'd need 04-11 data to make 04-14 predictions, which creates a timing gap I need to work around.\n\nFor now, I should focus on what's actually achievable—getting the pipeline working with existing data rather than trying to solve the full T+2 prediction problem. Let me run the script with a 15-minute timeout to test it out, and I'll adjust the training window to 2019-2020 to avoid any data leakage issues.","thinkingSignature":"e48c6530464b8cd65ac63bfe3e76a23a2fd4ae2f3f679d87841081c32222d0ed"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2wn0kh62jvfd_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/generate_predictions_lite.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"轻量级预测生成 - 训练2019-2020 + 预测2024-2026（避免全量加载OOM）\"\"\"\nimport os\nos.environ[\"OMP_NUM_THREADS\"] = \"4\"\nos.environ[\"MKL_NUM_THREADS\"] = \"4\"\nos.environ[\"OPENBLAS_NUM_THREADS\"] = \"4\"\n\nimport sys\nfrom pathlib import Path\nROOT = Path(\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\")\nsys.path.insert(0, str(ROOT))\n\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\nimport lightgbm as lgb\nimport gc\n\nOUTPUT_CSV = ROOT / \"data/ml_dataset_full/ml_predictions_live_latest.csv\"\n\nprint(\"=== [1/6] 读取已有预测 ===\")\nexisting = pd.read_csv(OUTPUT_CSV, usecols=[\"date\",\"symbol\",\"pred_rank\"])\nexisting[\"date\"] = pd.to_datetime(existing[\"date\"]).dt.date\nprint(f\"  已有: {len(existing)} 行, 最新: {existing['date'].max()}\")\n\nprint(\"=== [2/6] 加载universe180 ===\")\nuniverse_file = Path.home() / \".qlib/qlib_data/cn_data_long_2015_2026_180/instruments/universe180.txt\"\nstocks = []\nwith open(universe_file) as f:\n    for line in f:\n        parts = line.strip().split()\n        if len(parts) >= 3:\n            stocks.append(parts[0])\nprint(f\"  股票数: {len(stocks)}\")\n\nprint(\"=== [3/6] Qlib初始化 ===\")\nimport qlib\nfrom qlib.data import D\nqlib.init(provider_uri=str(Path.home() / \".qlib/qlib_data/cn_data_long_2015_2026_180\"), region=\"cn\")\n\nfields = [\"$close\",\"$open\",\"$high\",\"$low\",\"$volume\"]\n\ndef load_date_range(stocks_list, start, end, label=\"\"):\n    dates = D.calendar(start_time=start, end_time=end)\n    date_strs = [str(d)[:10] for d in dates]\n    print(f\"  [{label}] {len(date_strs)} days: {date_strs[0]}~{date_strs[-1]}\")\n    if not date_strs:\n        return pd.DataFrame()\n    \n    records = []\n    BATCH = 10\n    for i in range(0, len(date_strs), BATCH):\n        batch = date_strs[i:i+BATCH]\n        try:\n            df = D.features(stocks_list, fields, start_time=batch[0], end_time=batch[-1], freq=\"day\")\n            df = df.reset_index()\n            df.columns = [\"date\",\"symbol\"] + [f.replace(\"$\",\"\") for f in fields[1:]]\n            records.append(df)\n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"  批次 {i} 失败: {e}\")\n        if (i // BATCH) % 30 == 0:\n            print(f\"    {i+BATCH}/{len(date_strs)}\")\n    \n    if not records:\n        return pd.DataFrame()\n    data = pd.concat(records, ignore_index=True)\n    del records; gc.collect()\n    \n    for col in [\"close\",\"open\",\"high\",\"low\",\"volume\"]:\n        data[col] = pd.to_numeric(data[col], errors=\"coerce\")\n    data[\"date\"] = pd.to_datetime(data[\"date\"]).dt.date\n    data = data.dropna(subset=[\"date\",\"symbol\",\"close\"])\n    data = data[data[\"close\"] > 0]\n    return data\n\n# 训练期短但够用（2019-2020，2年），测试期覆盖所有\nprint(\"  加载训练数据(2019-2020)...\")\ntrain_data = load_date_range(stocks, \"2019-01-01\", \"2020-12-31\", \"TRAIN\")\ngc.collect()\n\nprint(\"  加载测试数据(2024-01~2026-04)...\")\ntest_data = load_date_range(stocks, \"2024-01-01\", \"2026-04-11\", \"TEST\")\ngc.collect()\n\nprint(f\"  训练集: {len(train_data)} 行, 测试集: {len(test_data)} 行\")\n\nprint(\"=== [4/6] 特征工程 ===\")\ndef add_features(df):\n    for n in [5, 10, 20]:\n        df[f\"roc{n}\"] = df.groupby(\"symbol\")[\"close\"].pct_change(n)\n    df[\"vol5\"] = df.groupby(\"symbol\")[\"volume\"].transform(lambda x: x.rolling(5, min_periods=1).mean())\n    df[\"vol_ratio\"] = df[\"volume\"] / df[\"vol5\"].replace(0, 1)\n    for n in [5, 10, 20]:\n        delta = df.groupby(\"symbol\")[f\"roc{n}\"].diff(n)\n        gain = delta.clip(lower=0).rolling(n, min_periods=1).mean()\n        loss = (-delta.clip(upper=0)).rolling(n, min_periods=1).mean()\n        df[f\"rsi{n}\"] = 100 - (100 / (1 + gain / loss.replace(0, 1e-10)))\n    return df\n\nfeature_cols = [\"close\",\"open\",\"high\",\"low\",\"volume\",\n                \"roc5\",\"roc10\",\"roc20\",\"vol_ratio\",\"rsi5\",\"rsi10\",\"rsi20\"]\n\ntrain_data = add_features(train_data)\ntest_data = add_features(test_data)\n\nfor df in [train_data, test_data]:\n    for c in feature_cols:\n        if c not in df.columns:\n            df[c] = 0\n    df[feature_cols] = df[feature_cols].fillna(0).replace([np.inf,-np.inf], 0)\n\nprint(\"=== [5/6] 训练+预测 ===\")\ntrain_data[\"label\"] = train_data.groupby(\"symbol\")[\"close\"].pct_change(5).fillna(0)\ntrain_data = train_data.dropna(subset=[\"date\"])\ntest_data[\"label\"] = test_data.groupby(\"symbol\")[\"close\"].pct_change(5).fillna(0)\ntest_data = test_data.dropna(subset=[\"date\"])\n\nX_train = train_data[feature_cols].values.astype(np.float32)\ny_train = train_data[\"label\"].values.astype(np.float32)\nX_test = test_data[feature_cols].values.astype(np.float32)\ndel train_data; gc.collect()\n\nlgb_train = lgb.Dataset(X_train, y_train, feature_name=feature_cols, free_raw_data=True)\nlgb_test = lgb.Dataset(X_test, feature_name=feature_cols, reference=lgb_train, free_raw_data=True)\ndel X_train, y_train; gc.collect()\n\nparams = {\n    \"objective\": \"mse\", \"num_leaves\": 31, \"learning_rate\": 0.05,\n    \"num_threads\": 4, \"verbose\": -1, \"min_data_in_leaf\": 100,\n}\nprint(\"  训练中...\")\nmodel = lgb.train(params, lgb_train, num_boost_round=100,\n                  valid_sets=[lgb_test], callbacks=[lgb.log_evaluation(50)])\nprint(\"  预测中...\")\ntest_data[\"pred\"] = model.predict(X_test)\ntest_data[\"pred_rank\"] = test_data.groupby(\"date\")[\"pred\"].rank(pct=True)\ndel X_test; gc.collect()\n\nprint(\"=== [6/6] 合并写入 ===\")\ncutoff = pd.Timestamp(\"2026-04-01\").date()\nnew_only = test_data[test_data[\"date\"] >= cutoff][[\"date\",\"symbol\",\"pred_rank\"]].copy()\nnew_only[\"date\"] = pd.to_datetime(new_only[\"date\"]).dt.strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\nprint(f\"  新增: {len(new_only)} 行\")\nprint(f\"  新增日期: {sorted(new_only['date'].unique())}\")\n\nif len(new_only) == 0:\n    print(\"  无新增，跳过\")\n    sys.exit(0)\n\ncombined = pd.concat([existing, new_only], ignore_index=True)\ncombined = combined.drop_duplicates(subset=[\"date\",\"symbol\"], keep=\"last\")\ncombined = combined.sort_values([\"date\",\"pred_rank\"], ascending=[True,False])\ncombined[\"date\"] = pd.to_datetime(combined[\"date\"]).dt.strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\ncombined.to_csv(OUTPUT_CSV, index=False)\nprint(f\"  ✅ 已保存: {OUTPUT_CSV}\")\nprint(f\"  总: {len(combined)} 行, {combined['date'].min()} ~ {combined['date'].max()}\")\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":35962,"output":2429,"cacheRead":35571,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73962,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776166191585,"responseId":"062d5831afb428f2efc479c6b7f53a9a"}}
