{"type":"message","id":"5c6e198b","parentId":"dfd4da56","timestamp":"2026-04-14T11:41:49.371Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about \"屈原列传\" which is the biography of Qu Yuan. This is a famous historical figure from ancient China, a poet and statesman who served during the Warring States period. He is best known for his poetry collection \"Li Sao\" and for his loyal service to the Chu kingdom, eventually drowning himself in the Miluo River in despair over political corruption.\n\nLet me give a brief, engaging response about Qu Yuan based on my knowledge, without needing to search for this.\n\nQu Yuan (340-278 BCE) was a poet and minister of the State of Chu during the Warring States period. \n\nHis literary masterpiece \"Li Sao\" is considered one of the greatest works of Chinese poetry, and his name is now forever linked to the Dragon Boat Festival, which commemorates his tragic suicide by drowning.","thinkingSignature":"12b5a7bb9fbc08cc3cb4b7a2bfde803aa94eb0bdfdf72411c820ba3ce4cb4397"},{"type":"text","text":"屈原（约公元前340—278年），名平，字原，楚国丹阳人，战国时期楚辞的创立者和代表作家。\n\n---\n\n## 生平\n\n少年得志，二十多岁即任楚怀王左徒（近似宰相），以内政外交兼修著称：内则明法度、举贤能，外则联齐抗秦，一时楚国大治。\n\n## 忠而被谤\n\n屈原主张联齐抗秦，触怒了贵族令尹子椒、上官大夫靳尚等人。怀王听信谗言，逐渐疏远屈原，最终放逐其于汉北（河南一带）。后来怀王被秦昭襄王骗入武关会盟，客死异乡。\n\n## 放逐与沉江\n\n顷襄王继位后，屈原再遭排挤，流放江南（今湖南沅湘流域）。公元前278年，秦将白起攻破郢都，楚顷襄王东迁，屈原悲愤交加，于农历五月初五投汨罗江而死。\n\n## 文学成就\n\n- **《离骚》**：中国浪漫主义文学的奠基之作，\"帝高阳之苗裔兮，朕朕情信芳……\"开篇即千古\n- **《九歌》《天问》《九章》**：构成了\"楚辞\"的主体\n- 创立\"香草美人\"的比兴传统，影响后世整个中国文学\n\n## 身后之名\n\n- **端午节**：民间于五月初五划龙舟、投粽子，即为纪念屈原\n- 1953年，世界和平理事会将屈原列为\"世界文化名人\"\n- \"路漫漫其修远兮，吾将上下而求索\"——成为中华民族精神的名句\n\n---\n\n司马迁在《史记·屈原贾生列传》中评价他：**\"推此志也，虽与日月争光可也。\"** 一个以死明志的诗人，从此与一个民族的节日永生。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":133,"output":567,"cacheRead":35571,"cacheWrite":56776,"totalTokens":93047,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776166882919,"re