{"type":"message","id":"55a6cdde","parentId":"3e8030ee","timestamp":"2026-04-14T12:58:04.881Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_f27i4orr2lco_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tushare 日频数据 → Qlib dump_update 增量更新\n\n流程:\n1. 从 Tushare 获取交易日历，找出 Qlib 最新日期之后的新日期\n2. 下载每日日频数据（OHLCV + 复权因子）\n3. 转换代码格式：000001.SZ → SZ000001（匹配 Qlib instruments 格式）\n4. 调用 Qlib dump_update 追加到现有数据\n\n用法:\n    python scripts/tushare_to_qlib_update.py --start 2026-03-05 --end 2026-03-22\n\"\"\"\nimport argparse\nimport os\nimport sys\nimport subprocess\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom datetime import datetime\nimport pandas as pd\nimport tushare as ts\nfrom tqdm import tqdm\n\nPROJECT_ROOT = Path(__file__).parent.parent.resolve()"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":40,"aggregated":"Tushare 日频数据 → Qlib dump_update 增量更新\n\n流程:\n1. 从 Tushare 获取交易日历，找出 Qlib 最新日期之后的新日期\n2. 下载每日日频数据（OHLCV + 复权因子）\n3. 转换代码格式：000001.SZ → SZ000001（匹配 Qlib instruments 格式）\n4. 调用 Qlib dump_update 追加到现有数据\n\n用法:\n    python scripts/tushare_to_qlib_update.py --start 2026-03-05 --end 2026-03-22\n\"\"\"\nimport argparse\nimport os\nimport sys\nimport subprocess\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom datetime import datetime\nimport pandas as pd\nimport tushare as ts\nfrom tqdm import tqdm\n\nPROJECT_ROOT = Path(__file__).parent.parent.resolve()","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776171484868}}
