{"type":"message","id":"7b3f46a3","parentId":"81ad0976","timestamp":"2026-04-14T12:58:25.586Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_somtno82akkq_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"37:EXTEND_END = \"2026-04-11\"  # 上周五，最新可交易日\n40:print(f\"Training model with test_end={EXTEND_END} (may take 10-20min)...\")\n45:        \"end_time\": EXTEND_END,\n50:        \"test\": (test_start, EXTEND_END),"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":47,"aggregated":"37:EXTEND_END = \"2026-04-11\"  # 上周五，最新可交易日\n40:print(f\"Training model with test_end={EXTEND_END} (may take 10-20min)...\")\n45:        \"end_time\": EXTEND_END,\n50:        \"test\": (test_start, EXTEND_END),","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776171505574}}
{"type":"message","id":"c3bee9c1","parentId":"7b3f46a3","timestamp":"2026-04-14T12:58:52.778Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the situation:\n\n1. `tushare_to_qlib_update.py` requires `--start` and `--end` args\n2. `generate_extended_predictions.py` has `EXTEND_END = \"2026-04-11\"` hardcoded - it needs to be updated to today's date\n\nFor the daily cron, I need a wrapper script that:\n1. Calculates the date range for `tushare_to_qlib_update.py`:\n   - `start`: Qlib latest date + 1 day\n   - `end`: today (or latest Tushare data date)\n2. Updates `EXTEND_END` in `generate_extended_predictions.py` or creates a variant that takes a date arg\n\n\n3. Runs both scripts sequentially\n\nI'll create a wrapper script that automatically detects the Qlib latest date and the latest Tushare data date, then calls both tools with the appropriate parameters, and schedule it as a cron job at 16:30 on weekdays.","thinkingSignature":"e280dc9f20679e02a4483aab23692ba2fef8e62e6111dfda2ab6ecad0af270a6"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了，写一个自动日期检测的 wrapper 脚本，然后加 cron：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_nl2orircdj76_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_daily_qlib_pipeline.sh","content":"#!/usr/bin/env bash\n# 每日 Qlib 数据管道 cron 脚本\n# 每天 16:30 自动执行：Tushare → Qlib → 预测生成\nset -euo pipefail\n\nROOT=\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\"\nLOG=\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/logs/daily_qlib_pipeline.log\"\n\nlog() {\n  echo \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] $*\" | tee -a \"$LOG\"\n}\n\ncd \"$ROOT\"\nlog \"=== 开始每日 Qlib 管道 ===\"\n\n# ============================================================\n# Step 1: 检测日期范围\n# ============================================================\nTODAY=$(date +%Y-%m-%d)\nPYTHON=\"/usr/bin/python3\"\n\n# 获取 Qlib 最新日期\nQLIB_LATEST=$($PYTHON -c \"\nimport sys; sys.path.insert(0, '$ROOT')\nimport qlib; from pathlib import Path\nqlib.init(provider_uri=str(Path.home() / '.qlib/qlib_data/cn_data_long_2015_2026_180'), region='cn')\nfrom qlib.data import D\ndates = D.calendar(start_time='2025-01-01', end_time='$TODAY')\nif dates is not None and len(dates) > 0:\n    latest = dates[-1]\n    print(str(latest)[:10])\nelse:\n    print('2026-01-01')\n\" 2>/dev/null)\n\n# 计算增量起始日期 = Qlib 最新日期 + 1 天\nSTART_DATE=$($PYTHON -c \"\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\nd = datetime.strptime('$QLIB_LATEST', '%Y-%m-%d') + timedelta(days=1)\nprint(d.strftime('%Y-%m-%d'))\n\" 2>/dev/null)\n\nlog \"Qlib 最新: $QLIB_LATEST → 增量起始: $START_DATE → 截止: $TODAY\"\n\n# 如果 Qlib 已是最新日期，无需更新\nif [[ \"$START_DATE\" > \"$TODAY\" ]]; then\n  log \"Qlib 数据已是最新，无需更新\"\nelse\n  # ============================================================\n  # Step 2: Tushare → Qlib\n  # ============================================================\n  log \"[Step 1] Tushare → Qlib ($START_DATE ~ $TODAY)\"\n  $PYTHON scripts/tushare_to_qlib_update.py --start \"$START_DATE\" --end \"$TODAY\" >> \"$LOG\" 2>&1\n  log \"[Step 1] 完成\"\nfi\n\n# ============================================================\n# Step 3: 生成预测\n# ============================================================\n# 更新 EXTEND_END 到今天\nNEW_EXTEND_END=$($PYTHON -c \"\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\n# 取最近5个交易日作为预测截止（避免今天盘中运行取到不完整数据）\nimport qlib; from pathlib import Path\nqlib.init(provider_uri=str(Path.home() / '.qlib/qlib_data/cn_data_long_2015_2026_180'), region='cn')\nfrom qlib.data import D\ndates = D.calendar(start_time='2025-01-01', end_time='$TODAY')\nif dates is not None and len(dates) >= 5:\n    # 取最近5个交易日中的倒数第5个（即5天前的那个交易日）\n    target = dates[-5]\n    print(str(target)[:10])\nelif dates is not None and len(dates) >= 2:\n    target = dates[-2]\n    print(str(target)[:10])\nelse:\n    print('$TODAY')\n\" 2>/dev/null)\n\nlog \"[Step 2] 生成预测 (test_end=$NEW_EXTEND_END)\"\n$PYTHON -c \"\nimport sys; sys.path.insert(0, '$ROOT')\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nscript_path = Path('$ROOT/scripts/generate_extended_predictions.py')\ncontent = script_path.read_text()\n\nold_line = None\nfor line in content.split('\\n'):\n    if line.startswith('EXTEND_END') and '=' in line:\n        old_line = line\n        break\n\nif old_line:\n    new_line = f'EXTEND_END = \\\"$NEW_EXTEND_END\\\"  # auto-updated $(date +%Y-%m-%d_%H:%M)'\n    content = content.replace(old_line, new_line)\n    script_path.write_text(content)\n    print(f'Updated EXTEND_END: {old_line.strip()} → {new_line.strip()}')\nelse:\n    print('WARNING: EXTEND_END line not found')\n\" >> \"$LOG\" 2>&1\n\n$PYTHON scripts/generate_extended_predictions.py >> \"$LOG\" 2>&1\nlog \"[Step 2] 预测生成完成\"\n\nlog \"=== 每日 Qlib 管道完成 ===\"\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":63885,"output":1310,"cacheRead":35571,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100766,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776171505587,"responseId":"062d6cf2859ed34ce701ccf4168c8467"}}
