{"type":"message","id":"94066ed1","parentId":"87b4aaf2","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:00:10.359Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the cron is added. Now let me test the script to make sure it works properly before tomorrow's 16:30 run. Let me do a quick dry run.Actually, since Qlib is at 04/10 and today is 04/14, the script should:1. START_DATE = 04/11 (Qlib latest + 1 day)\n2. END_DATE = 04/14 (today)\n3. Run tushare_to_qlib_update from 04/11 to 04/14\n4. Update EXTEND_END to 04/14 (Qlib latest after update)5. \n\nRun generate_extended_predictions. Since it's already past market hours at 8:42 PM, I should verify whether Tushare has already collected today's data or if I need to wait. I can run the script once to confirm everything works, though it might fail if there's no new data to process. Let me at least check that the date detection logic is functioning properly.","thinkingSignature":"89beb766651bcafbf6ae54f026d51f40c06f9b3f32de9478ac653f02f2f7241f"},{"type":"text","text":"Cron 加好了。验证一下脚本逻辑：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8744r5fsrj26_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 模拟测试日期检测逻辑\n/usr/bin/python3 -c \"\nimport sys, os\nsys.path.insert(0, '/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system')\nimport qlib\nfrom pathlib import Path\nqlib.init(provider_uri=str(Path.home() / '.qlib/qlib_data/cn_data_long_2015_2026_180'), region='cn')\nfrom qlib.data import D\n\ntoday = '2026-04-14'\ndates = D.calendar(start_time='2025-01-01', end_time=today)\nqlib_latest = str(dates[-1])[:10]\nprint(f'Qlib最新: {qlib_latest}')\n\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\nstart = datetime.strptime(qlib_latest, '%Y-%m-%d') + timedelta(days=1)\nprint(f'增量起始: {start.strftime(\\\"%Y-%m-%d\\\")}')\nprint(f'截止日期: {today}')\nprint(f'预测截止: {qlib_latest}')\n\n# 检查Tushare今天有没有数据\nimport tushare as ts\ntoken = os.getenv('TUSHARE_TOKEN', 'e3d8c68a414b9a84cbc49c637ec00875c7173a961eba98cff09c1afc')\npro = ts.pro_api(token)\ndf = pro.trade_cal(start_date='20260411', end_date='20260414')\nprint(f'Tushare交易日历:\\n{df[df.is_open==1]}')\n\" 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":68068,"output":582,"cacheRead":35571,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104221,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776171596026,"responseId":"062d6d4c1a42815f9477585b50d69245"}}
