{"type":"message","id":"0077f055","parentId":"0363ef38","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:05:35.352Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_vtzphpvcrcyr_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"def run_dump_update(csv_files: list[Path]):\n    \"\"\"执行 Qlib dump_update\"\"\"\n    if not csv_files:\n        print(\"  无 CSV 文件，跳过 dump_update\")\n        return\n\n    print(f\"\\n  执行 dump_update ({len(csv_files)} 个文件)...\")\n    \n    # dump_bin.py dump_update 命令格式\n    cmd = [\n        sys.executable, str(QLIB_DUMP_BIN), \"dump_update\",\n        \"--data_path\", str(csv_files[0].parent),  # 目录模式\n        \"--qlib_dir\", str(QLIB_DATA_DIR),\n        \"--freq\", \"day\",\n        \"--date_field_name\", \"date\",\n        \"--symbol_field_name\", \"symbol\",\n        \"--exclude_fields\", \"symbol,date\",\n        \"--max_workers\", \"8\",\n    ]\n    \n    print(f\"  命令: {' '.join(cmd[:6])} ...\")\n    result = subprocess.run(cmd, capture_output=True, text=True)\n    \n    # 输出最后几行"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":31,"aggregated":"def run_dump_update(csv_files: list[Path]):\n    \"\"\"执行 Qlib dump_update\"\"\"\n    if not csv_files:\n        print(\"  无 CSV 文件，跳过 dump_update\")\n        return\n\n    print(f\"\\n  执行 dump_update ({len(csv_files)} 个文件)...\")\n    \n    # dump_bin.py dump_update 命令格式\n    cmd = [\n        sys.executable, str(QLIB_DUMP_BIN), \"dump_update\",\n        \"--data_path\", str(csv_files[0].parent),  # 目录模式\n        \"--qlib_dir\", str(QLIB_DATA_DIR),\n        \"--freq\", \"day\",\n        \"--date_field_name\", \"date\",\n        \"--symbol_field_name\", \"symbol\",\n        \"--exclude_fields\", \"symbol,date\",\n        \"--max_workers\", \"8\",\n    ]\n    \n    print(f\"  命令: {' '.join(cmd[:6])} ...\")\n    result = subprocess.run(cmd, capture_output=True, text=True)\n    \n    # 输出最后几行","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776171935338}}
{"type":"message","id":"7dc89af0","parentId":"0077f055","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:05:50.389Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The command looks correct. It passes:\n- `--data_path`: the directory containing the CSV files\n- `--qlib_dir`: the Qlib data directory\n- `--freq`: day\n- `--date_field_name`: date\n- `--symbol_field_name`: symbol\n- `--exclude_fields`: symbol,date\n\nAnd the CSV format has columns: date, symbol, open, high, low, close, volume\n\nSo it should read symbol and date as the index, and open/high/low/close/volume as the feature fields. This should work.\n\nBut the features only went up to 04/08. Let me check if maybe the dump_update for 04/13 and 04/14 actually ran but processed the WRONG csv directory. \n\nI should look at what files actually got processed in the most recent run. The output said \"执行 dump_update (2 个文件)\" and \"✅ dump_update 成功\", but the skipped files were daily_20260413.csv and daily_20260414.csv. I need to figure out what happened to those files and whether the dump actually touched them or just left them untouched.\n\nLooking at the timestamps though - daily_20260413.csv shows Apr 13 00:53 and daily_20260414.csv shows Apr 14 21:00/21:01, which suggests these files already existed and weren't newly downloaded. That means dump_update processed them but either didn't update them or failed to process them correctly. Let me try running dump_update directly on just the 04/14 CSV to see what actually happens.","thinkingSignature":"e4a577631a975a796597e9ce3d26584c822e4894dbcdb935228aff5cf0866959"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ardmq3jtfmy8_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 直接运行 dump_update 验证 04/14 数据\ncd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system && \\\n/usr/bin/python3 qlib/scripts/dump_bin.py dump_update \\\n  --data_path data/tushare_raw \\\n  --qlib_dir ~/.qlib/qlib_data/cn_data_long_2015_2026_180 \\\n  --freq day \\\n  --date_field_name date \\\n  --symbol_field_name symbol \\\n  --exclude_fields symbol,date \\\n  --max_workers 4 2>&1 | grep -E \"更新|成功|失败|error|Error|SH600000|04-14|04-13\" | head -20","timeout":120}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":80108,"output":509,"cacheRead":35571,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116188,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776171935353,"responseId":"062d6ea3ac47e4164edf20dac22cd2b4"}}
