{"type":"message","id":"7956b668","parentId":"901a5871","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:12:03.857Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see. `/usr/local/bin/python3` points to Python 3.14. But `/usr/bin/python3` is Python 3.9 (system Python). When I run `/usr/bin/python3 scripts/tushare_to_qlib_update.py`, it uses Python 3.9 which works. But `qlib/scripts/dump_bin.py` is a standalone script that might use `#!/usr/bin/env python3` which would resolve to Python 3.14 (which might not have qlib installed).\n\nActually wait - the `cron_python.sh` uses `/usr/local/bin/python3` as the Python binary. \n\nSo the issue is that `sys.executable` in the `tushare_to_qlib_update.py` script points to Python 3.14 when run through the cron, which means `dump_bin.py` gets invoked with Python 3.14, but when I run it directly with `/usr/bin/python3` it's using Python 3.9 instead.\n\nWait, let me trace through this more carefully. The `cron_python.sh` sets `PYTHON_BIN` to `/usr/local/bin/python3` based on the `QUANT_CRON_PYTHON` variable, and that's what gets used to execute the script. So when `tushare_to_qlib_update.py` calls `sys.executable`, it's getting Python 3.14, not Python 3.9. I need to understand what `sys.executable` actually returns when the script is run through the cron wrapper versus when it's run directly with `/usr/bin/python3`.","thinkingSignature":"d1222381d12972437b3b98a3f9c0cfe7059d58b623644b56bb7c9393cc59cde6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2ltj06xddoao_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"/usr/bin/python3 -c \"import sys; print(sys.executable)\"\necho \"---\"\n/usr/local/bin/python3 -c \"import sys; print(sys.executable)\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"not found\"\necho \"---\"\n~/.openclaw/skills/../../../Library/pnpm/global/5/.pnpm/openclaw@2026.4.10_@emnapi+core@1.9.2_@emnapi+runtime@1.9.2_@napi-rs+canvas@0.1.97_@typ_a90ffd2929abe8f398b8e8e6d84b8ef0/node_modules/openclaw/skills/clawhub/SKILL.md 2>/dev/null\npython3 -c \"import sys; print(sys.executable)\" 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":97996,"output":529,"cacheRead":35571,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":134096,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776172310637,"responseId":"062d701bb9b5318b1450436c3c29a24f"}}
