{"type":"message","id":"c06893ae","parentId":"2ff56598","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:43:21.682Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see clearly:\n- Calendar: 1764 days (index 0~1763), last = 2026-04-14\n- SH600000 bin: 1760 values, index 0~1759, last date = CAL[1759] = 2026-04-08\n- SZ000001 bin: 1760 values, index 0~1759, last date = 2026-04-08\n- Missing dates: CAL[1760:] = 04-09, 04-10, 04-13, 04-14 (indices 1760, 1761, 1762, 1763)\n\n\n- The universe has 5499 stocks total, but the bin files for several of them don't actually exist (BJ920000, SZ302132) because they were listed in the universe but had no data at their respective start dates.\n\nThe issue is that `tushare_to_qlib_update.py` extended the calendar to 04-14 during a previous run, but the bin files themselves were never regenerated to match this new date range—they still only contain data through 04-08. The `append_missing_qlib_bins.py` script should fix this by detecting the gap between what the calendar claims (04-14) and what the bin files actually hold (04-08), then filling in the missing data for those intermediate dates.\n\nThere's also a bug in my script where I wrote `N_C_CAL` instead of `N_CAL` that needs correcting. Let me test this by reading the existing bin values to verify the state of the data.","thinkingSignature":"10fee4176cc57e260968e623f98dad2e138578925baa0b8b3f18ddca7a166c74"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qd760ccxdijs_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/append_missing_qlib_bins.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n直接追加 Qlib bin 缺失数据（04-09之后的4个交易日）\n修复：日历有 04-09~04-14 但 bin 文件只有 04-08\n\"\"\"\nimport sys\nimport warnings\nwarnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\n\nimport numpy as np\nimport pandas as pd\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom tqdm import tqdm\n\nQLIB_DATA_DIR = Path.home() / '.qlib/qlib_data/cn_data_long_2015_2026_180'\nUNIVERSE_FILE = QLIB_DATA_DIR / 'instruments' / 'universe180.txt'\nCAL_FILE = QLIB_DATA_DIR / 'calendars' / 'day.txt'\nRAW_DIR = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/tushare_raw')\n\nFIELDS = ['close', 'open', 'high', 'low', 'volume']\n\n# 读取日历\nwith open(CAL_FILE) as f:\n    CAL = [l.strip() for l in f]\nN_CAL = len(CAL)\nprint(f\"日历: {CAL[0]} ~ {CAL[-1]}, 共{N_CAL}天\")\n\n# 读取 universe\nwith open(UNIVERSE_FILE) as f:\n    instruments = [l.strip() for l in f if l.strip() and not l.startswith('#')]\nprint(f\"Universe: {len(instruments)} 只股票\")\n\n# 确认缺失日期\nMISSING_DATES = CAL[1760:]  # 04-09, 04-10, 04-13, 04-14\nprint(f\"缺失日期: {MISSING_DATES}\")\nprint(f\"缺失天数: {len(MISSING_DATES)}\")\n\n# 读取所有 CSV（增量）\nprint(\"\\n加载 CSV 数据...\")\nall_data = {}\nfor date_str in MISSING_DATES:\n    date_key = date_str.replace('-', '')  # '20260409'\n    csv_file = RAW_DIR / f'daily_{date_key}.csv'\n    if csv_file.exists():\n        df = pd.read_csv(csv_file)\n        data_dict = {}\n        for _, row in df.iterrows():\n            sym = row['symbol']\n            data_dict[sym] = {\n                'close':  float(row['close']),\n                'open':   float(row['open']),\n                'high':   float(row['high']),\n                'low':    float(row['low']),\n                'volume': float(row['volume']),\n            }\n        all_data[date_str] = data_dict\n        print(f\"  {date_str}: {len(data_dict)} 只股票\")\n    else:\n        print(f\"  {date_str}: CSV NOT FOUND\")\n\nprint(f\"\\n待追加: {len(all_data)} 个交易日\")\n\n# 验证 bin 末尾\nsym = instruments[0]\nsym_dir = QLIB_DATA_DIR / 'features' / sym.lower()\nbin_path = sym_dir / 'close.day.bin'\nwith open(bin_path, 'rb') as f:\n    data = f.read()\nn_vals = len(data) // 4 - 1\nstart_idx = int(np.frombuffer(data[:4], dtype='<f')[0])\nend_idx = start_idx + n_vals - 1\nprint(f\"\\nBIN 现状 ({sym}): index {start_idx}~{end_idx}, last={CAL[end_idx]}\")\nprint(f\"追加后: index {start_idx}~{end_idx + len(MISSING_DATES)}\")\n\n# ===== 追加每只股票的 bin 文件 =====\nprint(\"\\n追加 bin 数据（串行，避免并发）...\")\nok_count = 0\nskip_count = 0\nerror_count = 0\n\nfor idx, sym in enumerate(instruments):\n    sym_dir = QLIB_DATA_DIR / 'features' / sym.lower()\n    if not sym_dir.exists():\n        skip_count += 1\n        continue\n    \n    # 检查 bin 是否已完整\n    close_bin = sym_dir / 'close.day.bin'\n    if close_bin.exists():\n        size = close_bin.stat().st_size\n        n_existing = size // 4 - 1\n        if n_existing >= N_CAL:\n            # 已完整，跳过\n            ok_count += 1\n            continue\n    \n    # 追加每个字段\n    for fld in FIELDS:\n        bin_path = sym_dir / f'{fld}.day.bin'\n        if not bin_path.exists():\n            continue\n        \n        # 读取现有数据\n        with open(bin_path, 'rb') as f:\n            existing = f.read()\n        n_existing = len(existing) // 4 - 1\n        \n        # 如果已够长，跳过\n        if n_existing >= N_CAL:\n            continue\n        \n        # 构建新值\n        new_vals = []\n        for date_str in MISSING_DATES:\n            if date_str in all_data and sym in all_data[date_str]:\n                new_vals.append(float(all_data[date_str][sym].get(fld, np.nan)))\n            else:\n                new_vals.append(np.nan)\n        \n        # 写入追加\n        arr = np.array(new_vals, dtype='<f')\n        with open(bin_path, 'ab') as f:\n            arr.tofile(f)\n    \n    ok_count += 1\n    if (idx + 1) % 1000 == 0:\n        print(f\"  进度 {idx+1}/{len(instruments)}\")\n\nprint(f\"\\n完成: ok={ok_count}, skip={skip_count}, error={error_count}\")\n\n# 验证\nsym = instruments[0]\nsym_dir = QLIB_DATA_DIR / 'features' / sym.lower()\nbin_path = sym_dir / 'close.day.bin'\nwith open(bin_path, 'rb') as f:\n    data = f.read()\nn_vals = len(data) // 4 - 1\nstart_idx = int(np.frombuffer(data[:4], dtype='<f')[0])\nend_idx = start_idx + n_vals - 1\nprint(f\"\\n验证 {sym}: {n_vals} values, last index={end_idx}, last date={CAL[end_idx] if end_idx < N_CAL else 'OUT OF RANGE'}\")\nvalues = np.frombuffer(data[4:], dtype='<f')\nprint(f\"最后5个值: {values[-5:]}\")\nprint(f\"对应日期: {[CAL[start_idx + n_vals - 5 + i] for i in range(5)]}\")\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":67267,"output":1798,"cacheRead":39381,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108446,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776174169340,"responseId":"062d775d0bb911af96fb9bcec054cbd3"}}
