{"type":"message","id":"232ecc1e","parentId":"9d7394e4","timestamp":"2026-04-14T14:52:38.469Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now add the cron entry. The user wants it at 16:30 on weekdays. Let me add it to the crontab.","thinkingSignature":"b6316e793a423efc26f0c05e95308accb14816775907172093839cec0141e1c6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3cqnr9a16cuz_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"crontab -l 2>/dev/null | grep daily_qlib || echo \"未找到现有条目\"\necho \"---\"\n# 添加新 cron\n(crontab -l 2>/dev/null | grep -v \"run_daily_qlib_pipeline\"; \\\n echo \"30 16 * * 1-5 /bin/bash /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_daily_qlib_pipeline.sh >> /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/logs/daily_qlib_pipeline.log 2>&1\") | crontab -\necho \"✅ Cron 已添加\"\ncrontab -l 2>/dev/null | grep run_daily"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":98956,"output":203,"cacheRead":35569,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":134728,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776178351931,"responseId":"062d87b08145dfe3bad13163fa386f33"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1621bed4","parentId":"232ecc1e","timestamp":"2026-04-14T14:52:38.635Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_3cqnr9a16cuz_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"30 16 * * 1-5 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_daily_qlib_pipeline.sh >> /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/logs/daily_qlib_pipeline.log 2>&1\n---\n✅ Cron 已添加\n30 16 * * 1-5 /bin/bash /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_daily_qlib_pipeline.sh >> /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/logs/daily_qlib_pipeline.log 2>&1"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":61,"aggregated":"30 16 * * 1-5 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_daily_qlib_pipeline.sh >> /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/logs/daily_qlib_pipeline.log 2>&1\n---\n✅ Cron 已添加\n30 16 * * 1-5 /bin/bash /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_daily_qlib_pipeline.sh >> /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/logs/daily_qlib_pipeline.log 2>&1","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776178358621}}
{"type":"message","id":"2c45ba2d","parentId":"1621bed4","timestamp":"2026-04-14T14:52:57.375Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Cron is set up. Now let me update the memory file with the key lessons learned.","thinkingSignature":"a58dd9039244b2c9dfaca388421f18b1654b6d0f06ee764097b56c1fd8069572"},{"type":"text","text":"Cron 已添加。现在更新记忆，记录这次的问题和解决方案：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4hljz0ufxyp7_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat >> /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent/memory/2026-04-14.md << 'EOF'\n\n## Qlib 预测管道修复（彻底方案）\n\n### 根本原因\n1. **dump_update bug**：日历文件被人为更新到 04-14，但 bin 文件只写到 04-08。dump_update 认为\"日历已有 04-09~04-14\"就跳过写入，导致 bin 数据实际缺失。\n2. **DatasetH OOM**：generate_extended_predictions.py 使用 DatasetH 一次性加载 5499 只股票 × 多年数据，Mac mini 8GB RAM 不够。\n3. **Python 多进程冲突**：Qlib D.features() 内部使用 multiprocessing，与 Python 3.9/3.14 的 spawn 方法冲突。\n\n### 解决方案\n1. **bin 追加脚本** `append_missing_qlib_bins.py`：直接读取 CSV 数据并追加到 Qlib bin 文件末尾，修复 04-09~04-14 的 4 个交易日数据。\n   - 关键：symbol 转换规则 `BJ920000` → `920000.bj` 目录，`SH/SZ` → 小写\n   - CSV symbol 格式 `920000.BJ` 需要 normalize_symbol 转换\n2. **lite v3 脚本** `generate_predictions_lite_v3.py`：直接读 Qlib bin 文件，分日处理，不走 D.features() 避免多进程问题。使用 CSV 数据作为特征源。\n3. **Cron 管道** `run_daily_qlib_pipeline.sh`：每天 16:30 周一~周五自动执行。\n   - `30 16 * * 1-5`\n\n### 关键文件路径\n- 预测脚本：`.../personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/generate_predictions_lite_v3.py`\n- bin 追加：`.../personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/append_missing_qlib_bins.py`\n- 管道脚本：`.../personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_daily_qlib_pipeline.sh`\n- 预测输出：`.../personal-a-share-research-system/ml_predictions_live_latest.csv`\n- Qlib 数据：`~/.qlib/qlib_data/cn_data_long_2015_2026_180/`\n- Universe：`~/.qlib/qlib_data/cn_data_long_2015_2026_180/instruments/universe180.txt`\n\n### 教训\n- dump_update 写 bin 时，如果 CSV 已有数据但 bin 未正确写入，要看 bin 文件实际大小而非只看日历文件。\n- Qlib bin 格式（小端 float32，每 4 字节一个值）可以直接用 `np.frombuffer(data[4:], dtype='<f')` 读取。\n- BJ 股票 symbol 转换特殊：北京股票 `920000.BJ` → Qlib 目录 `920000.bj`，symbol 格式 `BJ920000`。\nEOF\necho \"记忆已更新\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":99305,"output":666,"cacheRead":35569,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":135540,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776178358637,"responseId":"062d87b6c7bac845980b8dcb1a1ea751"}}
