{"type":"message","id":"0a313d65","parentId":"a8a55be0","timestamp":"2026-04-14T14:53:06.066Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me reply to the user with a summary of what was accomplished.","thinkingSignature":"218c185bfe7ca1f6ff2da9eeccacd37feac65474de3dc8f0f9d267b0b288e64d"},{"type":"text","text":"搞定了！总结一下：\n\n**预测已恢复** ✅\n- `ml_predictions_live_latest.csv`：04-07 ~ 04-13 共 **27,439 条预测**\n- Lite v3 脚本：直接读 bin，5 个交易日全量 5488~5490 只/天，不再 OOM\n\n**彻底方案三件套：**\n| 脚本 | 作用 |\n|------|------|\n| `append_missing_qlib_bins.py` | 修复 Qlib bin 数据（这次手动跑过了） |\n| `generate_predictions_lite_v3.py` | 每日生成预测，直接读 bin 不走 DatasetH |\n| `run_daily_qlib_pipeline.sh` | cron 管道，每天 16:30 自动跑 |\n\n**Cron 已设置：** `30 16 * * 1-5`（周一至周五 16:30）\n\n下次清明节这种假期后，管道会自动检测并补数据，不用再手动修了。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":99990,"output":220,"cacheRead":35569,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":135779,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776178377493,"responseId":"062d87c962af7221ff6c671d44da7c4f"}}
