{"type":"message","id":"4b006929","parentId":"d2d2a5af","timestamp":"2026-04-14T15:01:07.702Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the situation. The cron runs at 8:30 AM, not real-time. And it failed because:\n1. The predictions were stuck at 04-03 (today is 04-14, so signal was 11 days stale)\n2. The cron ran at 8:30 AM today, but the predictions were still at 04-03, so the breadth paper trading was in \"stale\" mode (no new signals)\n\nNow the predictions are fixed (04-07 ~ 04-13), but the cron already ran this morning at 8:30 AM. \n\nFor real-time paper trading to work:\n\n\n1. The predictions need to be updated before the cron runs (needs predictions by ~8:00 AM)\n2. The cron needs to run during market hours for real-time execution\n\nThe cron is currently set at 8:30 AM on weekdays, which is before market open (9:30 AM), but it's using the OLD predictions (stuck at 04-03). Since we fixed the predictions at 9:00 PM tonight, they'll be ready for tomorrow's 8:30 AM cron run. But the user was asking about real-time execution, not just morning updates.\n\nTo actually run paper trading during market hours, I'd need a cron that runs at 9:00 AM or later and executes the strategy, though I'm constrained by Tushare's data availability—they update once daily around 16:00, so there's no true intra-day refresh. The real bottleneck is that predictions need to exist before the cron runs, and today's predictions won't be available until tomorrow.","thinkingSignature":"3ebc0ff4c024c143afa41db01ab781847c03b19c2252d8759c9e97e91d161709"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lj53fg3ujnc0_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 查看当前 cron 设置\ncrontab -l 2>/dev/null | grep -v \"^#\"\necho \"---\"\n# 查看今天 16:30 的 qlib pipeline 是否跑了\ncat /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/logs/daily_qlib_pipeline.log 2>/dev/null | tail -10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":106969,"output":424,"cacheRead":35569,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":142962,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776178852550,"responseId":"062d89a59ae999f33701a6c1a76c1629"}}
