{"type":"message","id":"c6c566c3","parentId":"85b894b0","timestamp":"2026-04-14T15:01:21.070Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the full picture:\n\n**Current Crons:**\n1. `30 8 * * 1-5` - breadth paper trading (morning, before market)\n2. `25 8 * * 1-5` - paper profiles v1 (morning)\n3. `35 9 * * 1-5` - precheck\n4. `30 13 * * 1-5` - intraday paper profiles (1:30 PM)\n5. `30 14 * * 1-5` - intraday paper profiles (2:30 PM)\n\n\n6. `10 16 * * 1-5` - dashboard portal\n7. `30 16 * * 1-5` - daily qlib pipeline (just added today)\n8. `0,30 9-11,13-15 * * 1-5` - sector sync + market pulse\n\nThe core issue is that the morning crons at 8:30 ran with stale predictions stuck at 04-03, so when the qlib pipeline finally updated today with 04-13 predictions, the afternoon intraday runs at 1:30 and 2:30 PM still used outdated data.\n\nNow I need to check what happened with today's 1:30 and 2:30 PM intraday runs to understand the full scope of the problem.","thinkingSignature":"a1698dcded9bc5902821340058bb837aea9fb3c91a7766a40ba19cf11a277cd2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ypa0t50qutxh_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 查看今天 13:30 和 14:30 intraday cron 的日志\ngrep -n \"2026-04-14 13:3\\|2026-04-14 14:3\\|today_trade\\|2026-04-14 08:3\" \\\n  /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/logs/paper_profiles_cron.log 2>/dev/null | head -20\necho \"---\"\n# 检查 intraday 模式是如何使用 predictions 的\ngrep -n \"ml_predictions_live\\|PREDICTIONS\\|predictions.*latest\\|intraday\" \\\n  /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_paper_trading_profiles_auto_v1.sh 2>/dev/null | head -10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":108167,"output":481,"cacheRead":35569,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":144217,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776178867822,"responseId":"062d89b4