{"type":"message","id":"c6061a4c","parentId":"c83ff6f5","timestamp":"2026-04-14T15:01:43.498Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The daily_qlib_pipeline.log is empty. That means the 16:30 cron hasn't run yet (it's 23:00 now, so it should have run but maybe the log was overwritten).\n\nWait, looking at the cron schedule again - `30 16 * * 1-5` - this is Monday to Friday at 16:30. Today is Tuesday 04-14, so it SHOULD have run. But the log file is empty.\n\nLet me check if the cron ran and what happened.","thinkingSignature":"12770b58a2a1558d6d7eb051f1aef58c5fe05e75224c1b7deb051808b100256d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_aj67z07536fi_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查 16:30 cron 是否实际执行了\ncat /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/logs/daily_qlib_pipeline.log 2>/dev/null\necho \"File size: $(wc -c < /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/logs/daily_qlib_pipeline.log 2>/dev/null)\"\necho \"---\"\n# 检查 cron 执行日志\ngrep \"daily_qlib\\|2026-04-14 16\" /var/log/system.log 2>/dev/null | tail -5\n# 或者看 crontab 的时间戳\nstat /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/logs/daily_qlib_pipeline.log 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":109136,"output":276,"cacheRead":35569,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":144981,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776178895144,"responseId":"062d89cf11aa051ca98d571ffa315431"}}
