{"type":"message","id":"683293b8","parentId":"1584e046","timestamp":"2026-04-14T15:07:53.849Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me summarize what happened and what the current state is:\n\n**What happened today:**\n1. Morning 08:30 - breadth cron ran with OLD predictions (04-03) → signal was stale, positions held but not traded\n2. 13:30 and 14:30 - intraday crons ran but data was stale (a_stock_history.csv at 04-10)\n3. 16:30 - daily_qlib_pipeline cron was added but likely didn't execute successfully (log file empty)\n4. 21:00-23:00 - I fixed the predictions manually, generated 04-07~04-13 predictions\n5. 23:05 - Manually ran breadth_paper_trading with fresh predictions → SELL ALL signal, NAV updated to 0.9970\n \nTomorrow morning at 08:30, the breadth cron will pick up the fresh 04-13 predictions and execute properly. The intraday crons are working but hitting a data staleness issue—the market data is still showing 04-10 when the script expects 04-14. I need to trace where this historical data file is coming from and either update it or switch to using Tushare for real-time price lookups instead of relying on the CSV file.","thinkingSignature":"87d5dfc4c8d4ba5956b39e70f53ebf360aa43488a9626bff33c66e9ed2a17aec"},{"type":"text","text":"现在状态清楚了。让我总结一下今天的情况和修复进展：\n\n**今天发生了什么：**\n| 时间 | 事件 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 08:30 | breadth cron（预测停在 04-03） | ❌ 信号过期，11天滞后 |\n| 13:30 / 14:30 | 日内 crons | ❌ price数据停在04-10，报错 |\n| 16:30 | daily_qlib_pipeline cron | ⚠️ 未执行（日志为空） |\n| 23:05 | 手动修复预测 + 重跑 breadth | ✅ 卖出全部8只，净值0.9970 |\n\n**当前状态：**\n- `ml_predictions_live_latest.csv` → 04-07~04-13 ✅（明天08:30的cron会用到）\n- breadth_aggressive → 清仓了（因为今天宽度信号弱）\n\n**还剩一个问题：** 日内 crons（13:30/14:30）报 `stale_price_source: market_trade_date=20260410`，`a_stock_history.csv` 数据停在了 04-10。需要修复数据源。要一起修吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":118373,"output":512,"cacheRead":35569,"cac