tant: 预测已恢复到 04-13 ✅\n\n现在设置每日 cron（收盘后 16:30 自动跑）：\n[non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): #!/usr/bin/env bash\n# 每日 Qlib 数据管道 cron 脚本\n# 每天 16:30 (周一~周五) 自动执行：Tushare → Qlib → 预测生成\nset -euo pipefail\n\nROOT=\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\"\nPYTHON=\"/usr/bin/python3\"\nLOG=\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/logs/daily_qlib_pipeline.log\"\n\nlog() {\n  echo \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] $*\" | tee -a \"$LOG\"\n}\n\ncd \"$ROOT\"\nlog \"=== 开始每日 Qlib 管道 ===\"\n\n# ============================================================\n# Step 1: 检测日期范围\n# ============================================================\nTODAY=$(date +%Y-%m-%d)\n\n# 获取 Qlib 最新日期\nQLIB_LATEST=$($PYTH...\n- Assistant: [non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (write): Successfully wrote 2695 bytes to /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_daily_qlib_pipeline.sh\n- Assistant: [non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (write): Successfully wrote 1051 bytes to /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_daily_qlib_pipeline.sh\n- Assistant: [non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): 30 16 * * 1-5 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_daily_qlib_pipeline.sh >> /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/logs/daily_qlib_pipeline.log 2>&1\n---\n✅ Cron 已添加\n30 16 * * 1-5 /bin/bash /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_daily_qlib_pipeline.sh >> /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/logs/daily_qlib_pipeline.log 2>&1\n- Assistant: Cron 已添加。现在更新记忆，记录这次的问题和解决方案：\n[non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): 记忆已更新\n- Assistant: 搞定了！总结一下：\n\n**预测已恢复** ✅\n- `ml_predictions_live_latest.csv`：04-07 ~ 04-13 共 **27,439 条预测**\n- Lite v3 脚本：直接读 bin，5 个交易日全量 5488~5490 只/天，不再 OOM\n\n**彻底方案三件套：**\n| 脚本 | 