{"type":"message","id":"19debdab","parentId":"e3e176c9","timestamp":"2026-04-14T15:18:37.468Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user sent \"修\" (fix) again, but I already did the fix in my previous response. The message seems to be sent at the same timestamp as the previous one (23:08:24), so it might be a duplicate or the user is confirming they want me to proceed. \n\nSince I already completed the fix in my previous turn (updated predictions, synced files, ran download_tushare, fixed OUTPUT_FILE path), let me confirm the results to the user.","thinkingSignature":"6c139f81d539bcf4e9b7f53ca4b2454ec3849504aaf0a1f55def4045f1967e52"},{"type":"text","text":"已经修完了！快速总结：\n\n**今天修复了 3 个问题：**\n\n| 问题 | 原因 | 修复 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 预测停在 04-03 | Qlib bin 数据缺失 + Lite v3 路径 bug | 补 bin 数据 + 修复输出路径 |\n| 价格停在 04-10 | `download_tushare.py` 没跑 | 手动触发，已更新到 04-14 ✅ |\n| 预测文件路径混乱 | 两个不同路径 | 统一输出到 `data/ml_dataset_full/` |\n\n**当前状态：**\n- 预测：04-13（27,439 条）✅\n- 价格：04-14（11.2M 条）✅\n- Cron 16:30 明天会自动跑（下载 → Qlib 更新 → 生成预测）\n\n**还有一个问题待解决：** 日内模拟盘（13:30/14:30 的 `PAPER_PROFILE_RUN_MODE=intraday`）脚本 OOM 了，正在跑的那个被系统 SIGKILL 了。这个脚本加载了太多历史数据，需要优化。要一起修吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":133,"output":332,"cacheRead":35569,"cacheWrite":24257,"totalTokens":60291,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776179905406,"responseId":"062d8dc1fb449213e65852572d6b11ae"}}
