{"type":"message","id":"a131c8cc","parentId":"df36a138","timestamp":"2026-04-14T15:20:11.042Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is clear: the intraday cron runs with `PAPER_PROFILE_RUN_MODE=intraday` but doesn't set `PAPER_PROFILE_RUN_HEAVY_REPORTS=0`. This means it still runs all the heavy report generation scripts (`generate_today_stock_strategy_report.py`, `generate_control_tower_daily.py`, etc.) which load massive amounts of data.\n\nLet me fix this by adding `PAPER_PROFILE_RUN_HEAVY_REPORTS=0` to the intraday crons. This will skip the heavy reports that aren't needed during intraday hours.\n\nBut wait - let me also check what the `cron_python.sh` script does and how much memory each subprocess uses.","thinkingSignature":"735958ef0495526264a7964f570a65b8de8037f1456d1772dfda7bc06e080cfb"},{"type":"text","text":"找到问题了！日内模式仍然在跑所有 heavy reports（`generate_today_stock_strategy_report.py` 等），这些脚本加载大量数据导致 OOM。\n\n快速修复——给日内 cron 加上 `PAPER_PROFILE_RUN_HEAVY_REPORTS=0`：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_h4135om5uoe2_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 修复日内 cron，跳过 heavy reports\ncrontab -l 2>/dev/null | sed 's|PAPER_PROFILE_RUN_MODE=intraday bash scripts/run_paper_trading_profiles_auto_v1.sh|PAPER_PROFILE_RUN_MODE=intraday PAPER_PROFILE_RUN_HEAVY_REPORTS=0 bash scripts/run_paper_trading_profiles_auto_v1.sh|g' | crontab -\necho \"---\"\ncrontab -l 2>/dev/null | grep \"13.*intraday\\|14.*intraday\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":33325,"output":335,"cacheRead":35569,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69229,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776180001179,"responseId":"062d8e21d4227c4cf551cd829738bde3"}}
