{"type":"message","id":"5c9c170b","parentId":"3b68ecfc","timestamp":"2026-04-14T15:33:36.533Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! The chunked reading is working:\n- `load_price_history`: 1.5GB peak (instead of loading all 11M rows at once)\n- `load_latest_daily_basic`: 1.3GB peak\n- Combined peak: 4GB (instead of potentially 8GB+ before)\n\nThis is much better! Now the OOM issue should be resolved. The peak memory is still high at 4GB but it's within the 16GB available RAM.\n\nWait, actually 4GB peak is still quite high. But since the process was getting SIGKILL'd before (probably at ~5-6GB), and we now have 16GB system RAM with probably 10GB+ available, this should work.","thinkingSignature":"4b92184df6d816e87132955fd388edc560021c5faeb4a1a9809e2e088f1d681e"},{"type":"text","text":"修复验证通过！峰值内存从可能超 8GB 降到 4GB，安全了。\n\n现在启动 GPT-5.4 做全面系统检查：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fn9wp7476dj0_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"全面检查量化系统的堵点和链路不通的地方\n\n## 系统概述\n位于 `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/`\n这是一个 A 股量化研究系统，包含：\n- **模拟盘**（paper trading）：8个账号（aggressive、balanced、defensive、breadth_aggressive、alpha55等）\n- **信号生成**：宽度信号（breadth）、小市值筹码、财务因子\n- **数据管道**：Tushare → Qlib → 预测模型 → 模拟盘\n\n## 关键文件\n- 预测：`data/ml_dataset_full/ml_predictions_live_latest.csv`（27k条，最新04-13）\n- 价格：`/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/data/a_stock_history.csv`（11M行）\n- Qlib数据：`~/.qlib/qlib_data/cn_data_long_2015_2026_180/`\n- Cron配置：\n  - 08:30 breadth paper trading\n  - 13:30 / 14:30 intraday paper profiles\n  - 16:30 daily qlib pipeline\n- 核心脚本：\n  - `scripts/tushare_to_qlib_update.py` — Tushare → Qlib\n  - `scripts/generate_predictions_lite_v3.py` — Qlib → 预测\n  - `scripts/generate_live_smallcap_candidates.py` — 小市值候选（已修复OOM）\n  - `scripts/prepare_paper_orders_v1.py` — 信号→订单\n  - `scripts/run_breadth_paper_trading.py` — 宽度信号模拟盘\n  - `scripts/run_paper_trading_profiles_v1.sh` — 多账号模拟盘\n  - `scripts/run_daily_qlib_pipeline.sh` — 每日管道\n\n## 检查要求\n\n请逐一检查以下方面，找出堵点和问题：\n\n1. **数据链路完整性**：Tushare → Qlib → 预测 → 模拟盘，每个环节是否通畅？日期是否衔接？有无断层？\n\n2. **Cron 调度问题**：各 cron 的执行时间是否合理？依赖关系是否正确？有无重复执行或遗漏？\n\n3. **OOM/性能隐患**：还有哪些脚本会一次性加载大文件？有没有内存风险？\n\n4. **信号路径**：信号从生成到模拟盘执行，路径是否最短？有无冗余或无效环节？\n\n5. **数据一致性问题**：不同目录的预测/价格文件是否统一？有没有\"两个真相\"的风险？\n\n6. **Stale 数据风险**：哪些环节可能产生 stale 数据？停更时间窗口是多久？\n\n7. **API 依赖风险**：哪些环节依赖外部 API（Tushare等）？有没有备用方案？\n\n请输出：\n- 问题清单（按严重程度：P0/P1/P2）\n- 每个问题的描述、原因、影响\n- 建议的修复方案\n- 优先级建议（先修什么）","runtime":"subagent","model":"beecode/gpt-5.4","timeoutSeconds":600,"mode":"run"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":51922,"output":875,"cacheRead":35569,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88366,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776180793867,"responseId":"062d913a0781882b85af522e746929f3"}}
