{"type":"message","id":"c0e0684f","parentId":"0d92e293","timestamp":"2026-04-14T15:39:30.918Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see that the pipeline script has a hardcoded `--start \"2026-04-01\"` for tushare_to_qlib_update. This is fine for catching up but not ideal. But more importantly, the `generate_predictions_lite_v3.py` now has dynamic PRED_END.\n\nHowever, I notice the pipeline script uses `TODAY=$(date +%Y-%m-%d)` which would be today's date. Let me verify the time order issue by checking what cron runs first.\n\nActually, let me just do a quick summary:\n\n1. P0-1 (hardcoded PRED_END) → ✅ Fixed (now uses dynamic CAL[-1])\n\n\n2. P0-2 (time order) → Actually not a bug, it's by design. The 08:30 breadth paper uses yesterday's predictions (generated at yesterday's 16:30). This is correct behavior for a paper trading system.\n\nSo the cron schedule makes sense: the breadth paper runs at 08:30 using predictions from the previous day's 16:30, then the Qlib pipeline runs at 16:30 to generate today's predictions for tomorrow morning. The 08:30 trade → 16:30 data → next 08:30 trade cycle is working as intended.\n\nThe \"lag\" GPT mentioned is actually just the expected delay between market close and when new predictions become available—which is normal for EOD systems. The real P0 issues are the hardcoded date and possibly the missing 04-14 predictions from today's pipeline run.","thinkingSignature":"b1a23bdc5b02646aeb8f4f3774463bfeee86b5347007782f1090ec6c2ee0e504"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ut87ggcjmc1d_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 验证时间顺序：明早 08:30 的 breadth paper 会用哪天的预测？\necho \"=== 预测文件最新日期 ===\"\n/usr/bin/python3 -c \"\nimport pandas as pd\ndf = pd.read_csv('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/ml_dataset_full/ml_predictions_live_latest.csv')\nprint('预测最新日期:', df['date'].max(), '共', len(df), '条')\nprint('包含日期:', sorted(df['date'].unique()))\n\"\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Cron 时间线 ===\"\necho \"16:30 (今天) → run_daily_qlib_pipeline → 生成 04-14 预测\"\necho \"08:30 (明天) → cron_breadth_paper_trading → 读取 04-14 预测 ✅\"\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Qlib 日历最新 ===\"\nhead -1 /Users/ling/.qlib/qlib_data/cn_data_long_2015_2026_180/calendars/day.txt\ntail -1 /Users/ling/.qlib/qlib_data/cn_data_long_2015_2026_180/calendars/day.txt"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54392,"output":590,"cacheRead":35391,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90373,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776181155624,"responseId":"062d92a42f457c4a478378e69a596cf2"}}
